00:18:00,880 --> 00:18:02,160
[SPEAKER_01] ne mori imati visoku,

361
00:18:02,160 --> 00:18:03,500
[SPEAKER_01] može biti podhlađeno.

362
00:18:03,500 --> 00:18:07,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ako je spavao,

363
00:18:07,119 --> 00:18:07,980
[SPEAKER_01] ako bi ga probudili,

364
00:18:07,980 --> 00:18:09,339
[SPEAKER_01] on je normalan, veseo,

365
00:18:09,339 --> 00:18:11,740
[SPEAKER_01] to najčešće ne upuče

366
00:18:11,740 --> 00:18:13,640
[SPEAKER_01] na nikakvo ozbiljno stanje.

367
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:17,140
[SPEAKER_00] Okej, sreća u...

368
00:18:17,140 --> 00:18:18,339
[SPEAKER_00] Nije čak ni nesreće,

369
00:18:18,339 --> 00:18:20,019
[SPEAKER_00] ali u toj situaciji što ja nisam

370
00:18:20,019 --> 00:18:21,180
[SPEAKER_00] ni liječnica,

371
00:18:21,180 --> 00:18:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] ni očito dovoljno informirana,

372
00:18:22,420 --> 00:18:24,079
[SPEAKER_00] pa mi nije uopće bila asocijacija

373
00:18:24,079 --> 00:18:26,440
[SPEAKER_00] neka teška stanja,

374
00:18:26,440 --> 00:18:28,319
[SPEAKER_00] nego jednostavno neka panika,

375
00:18:28,319 --> 00:18:29,319
[SPEAKER_00] što se događa,

376
00:18:29,319 --> 00:18:31,299
[SPEAKER_00] dok će sad padat ta temperatura,

377
00:18:31,519 --> 00:18:34,859
[SPEAKER_00] nekada prije to nisam iskusila.

378
00:18:34,859 --> 00:18:36,440
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je isto,

379
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:38,200
[SPEAKER_00] moj neki zaključak na to sve bio,

380
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:39,059
[SPEAKER_00] da je vjerojatno,

381
00:18:39,059 --> 00:18:41,799
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam to sebi tako objasnila,

382
00:18:41,799 --> 00:18:43,059
[SPEAKER_00] osjetljiviji na taj,

383
00:18:43,059 --> 00:18:44,339
[SPEAKER_00] konkretno taj sirup,

384
00:18:44,339 --> 00:18:45,859
[SPEAKER_00] koji je poznat kao ono,

385
00:18:45,859 --> 00:18:46,819
[SPEAKER_00] jači malo.

386
00:18:46,819 --> 00:18:48,900
[SPEAKER_00] I onda mu malo manje doziram,

387
00:18:48,900 --> 00:18:50,960
[SPEAKER_00] ili ne uzimam više taj,

388
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:53,619
[SPEAKER_00] uglavnom sve je na kraju dobro završilo,

389
00:18:53,619 --> 00:18:55,839
[SPEAKER_00] ali malo jesam paničar u tim situacijama.

390
00:18:55,839 --> 00:18:57,400
[SPEAKER_01] A super ste postupili,

391
00:18:57,400 --> 00:18:58,700
[SPEAKER_01] znači utoplili ste ga,

392
00:18:58,700 --> 00:19:00,059
[SPEAKER_01] tu vam je jedino rješenje,

393
00:19:00,059 --> 00:19:01,099
[SPEAKER_01] ako je stvarno niska,

394
00:19:01,099 --> 00:19:03,099
[SPEAKER_01] da vi date tople napitke,

395
00:19:03,099 --> 00:19:04,640
[SPEAKER_01] utopliti ga dekicom,

396
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:06,480
[SPEAKER_01] dati nešto za pojesti,

397
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:08,099
[SPEAKER_01] nekad može biti niska temperatura,

398
00:19:08,099 --> 00:19:09,500
[SPEAKER_01] isto ako i šećer niski,

399
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:10,500
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, nije jeo,

400
00:19:10,500 --> 00:19:11,700
[SPEAKER_01] znači u hipoglikemii,

401
00:19:11,700 --> 00:19:12,779
[SPEAKER_01] tad bi bio bljed,

402
00:19:12,779 --> 00:19:14,220
[SPEAKER_01] više orošen znojem,

403
00:19:14,220 --> 00:19:17,119
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda može biti isto nisko izmjereno.

404
00:19:18,519 --> 00:19:26,680
[SPEAKER_00] Vratimo se onda sad

405
00:19:26,680 --> 00:19:29,400
[SPEAKER_00] na spomenute febrilne konvulzije.

406
00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:31,519
[SPEAKER_00] Vidjela sam negdje po novom

407
00:19:31,519 --> 00:19:33,400
[SPEAKER_00] da se to zove sad kako?

408
00:19:33,400 --> 00:19:36,039
[SPEAKER_01] Po novoj klasifikaciji

409
00:19:36,039 --> 00:19:37,940
[SPEAKER_01] febrilne konvulzije se zovu

410
00:19:37,940 --> 00:19:41,119
[SPEAKER_01] jednostavni motorički napadaj u temperaturi.

411
00:19:41,119 --> 00:19:45,660
[SPEAKER_00] Kako prepoznati što kad se dogodi prvi put

412
00:19:45,660 --> 00:19:47,400
[SPEAKER_00] i kad se to najčešće

413
00:19:48,140 --> 00:19:49,140
[SPEAKER_00] u pravilu javlja?

414
00:19:49,140 --> 00:19:50,140
[SPEAKER_00] I što je uopće?

415
00:19:50,140 --> 00:19:52,920
[SPEAKER_01] Da, znači to su nam jednostavni

416
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:55,440
[SPEAKER_01] motorički napadi u temperaturi.

417
00:19:55,440 --> 00:19:58,319
[SPEAKER_01] Javljaju se najčešće kod male djece,

418
00:19:58,319 --> 00:20:00,019
[SPEAKER_01] onda su to tipični.

419
00:20:00,019 --> 00:20:02,140
[SPEAKER_01] To je između šest mjeseci

420
00:20:02,140 --> 00:20:04,200
[SPEAKER_01] i pet godina života.

421
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:07,799
[SPEAKER_01] Obično uslijed neke virusne bolesti,

422
00:20:07,799 --> 00:20:09,299
[SPEAKER_01] rijeđe bakterijske,

423
00:20:09,299 --> 00:20:11,299
[SPEAKER_01] kada imamo nagli porast temperature.

424
00:20:11,980 --> 00:20:14,640
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, nije nužna da ona poraste na 40.

425
00:20:14,640 --> 00:20:18,619
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ali nagli neke normale 36 sa 7

426
00:20:18,619 --> 00:20:20,839
[SPEAKER_01] da skoči na 38 sa 3

427
00:20:20,839 --> 00:20:23,420
[SPEAKER_01] zbog toga što je još nezrelost

428
00:20:23,420 --> 00:20:24,740
[SPEAKER_01] živčanih puteva.

429
00:20:24,740 --> 00:20:27,720
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, stanice živčani su prepodražljive.

430
00:20:28,140 --> 00:20:30,019
[SPEAKER_01] Može se desiti takav napad.

431
00:20:30,019 --> 00:20:33,839
[SPEAKER_01] Roditeljima to izgleda izuzetno dramatično,

432
00:20:33,839 --> 00:20:36,039
[SPEAKER_01] jer razni moji pacijenti

433
00:20:36,039 --> 00:20:37,720
[SPEAKER_01] koji su to doživili prvi puta,

434
00:20:37,720 --> 00:20:40,599
[SPEAKER_01] to ti izgleda taj čas ako nisi upoznati,

435
00:20:40,599 --> 00:20:43,019
[SPEAKER_01] ne znaš kao da djete odlazi.

436
00:20:43,019 --> 00:20:46,240
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to su ritmični trzevi ekstremiteta.

437
00:20:46,240 --> 00:20:49,180
[SPEAKER_01] Djete zapravo zna imat ukočen pogled,

438
00:20:49,180 --> 00:20:52,579
[SPEAKER_01] po bljedi ili ima onako lila okrajine.

439
00:20:52,579 --> 00:20:54,680
[SPEAKER_01] Izgleda kao da uopće ne diše,

440
00:20:54,680 --> 00:20:55,799
[SPEAKER_01] pjenica na ustima.

441
00:20:55,960 --> 00:20:57,700
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to izgleda stvarno dramatično

442
00:20:57,700 --> 00:20:59,500
[SPEAKER_01] i koliko god to traje minutu, dvije,

443
00:20:59,500 --> 00:21:02,759
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim da čovjeku koji je tad sam kod kuće,

444
00:21:02,759 --> 00:21:04,920
[SPEAKER_01] to izgleda kao vječnost.

445
00:21:04,920 --> 00:21:09,859
[SPEAKER_01] Tada je bitno zapravo znati da pomognemo djetetu.

446
00:21:09,859 --> 00:21:11,480
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, šta je bitno?

447
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:12,940
[SPEAKER_01] Bitno je staviti ga na bok,

448
00:21:12,940 --> 00:21:14,339
[SPEAKER_01] znači raskomotiti,

449
00:21:14,339 --> 00:21:16,619
[SPEAKER_01] jer obično ima temperaturu povišenu

450
00:21:16,619 --> 00:21:19,079
[SPEAKER_01] i skinuti te temperature visoke.

451
00:21:19,079 --> 00:21:22,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ono što je bitno,

452
00:21:22,480 --> 00:21:24,920
[SPEAKER_01] dok se mi snađemo to najčešće,

453
00:21:24,980 --> 00:21:27,380
[SPEAKER_01] naravno pozvati hitnu prođe spontano.

454
00:21:27,380 --> 00:21:31,640
[SPEAKER_01] No, međutim, ima djece kojoj se to ponavlja.

455
00:21:31,640 --> 00:21:35,119
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, tada obično su roditelji educirani,

456
00:21:35,119 --> 00:21:38,079
[SPEAKER_01] ta djeca su i neuropedijatriski obrađena.

457
00:21:38,079 --> 00:21:40,940
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, uvijek se kada se ponavljaju snima EEG,

458
00:21:40,940 --> 00:21:44,480
[SPEAKER_01] da se vidi da je sve uredno s moždanom aktivnosti

459
00:21:44,480 --> 00:21:45,559
[SPEAKER_01] u zdravom stanju.

460
00:21:45,559 --> 00:21:48,160
[SPEAKER_01] i zapravo, kod takvih situacija,

461
00:21:48,160 --> 00:21:50,119
[SPEAKER_01] osim skidanja temperature,

462
00:21:50,119 --> 00:21:53,720
[SPEAKER_01] se preporuča i dati klizmica diazepama

463
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:57,180
[SPEAKER_01] ili po novom, možda jednostavnije za primjenu,

464
00:21:57,180 --> 00:21:58,440
[SPEAKER_01] nekad je bukolam,

465
00:21:58,440 --> 00:22:00,700
[SPEAKER_01] to je znači tekućenica koja se daje

466
00:22:00,700 --> 00:22:03,880
[SPEAKER_01] i onda je to direktna resorpcija u obraz.

467
00:22:04,119 --> 00:22:05,680
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, postoje i doze,

468
00:22:05,680 --> 00:22:07,039
[SPEAKER_01] ovisno od dobi djeteta,

469
00:22:07,039 --> 00:22:09,440
[SPEAKER_01] ali to se sve lijepo oni konzultiraju

470
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:10,599
[SPEAKER_01] s neuropedijatrom,

471
00:22:10,599 --> 00:22:12,900
[SPEAKER_01] to ne bi da se daje na svoju ruku

472
00:22:12,900 --> 00:22:13,980
[SPEAKER_01] bez konzultacije.

473
00:22:13,980 --> 00:22:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

474
00:22:14,539 --> 00:22:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] Baš ste mi sad odgovorili na podpitanje

475
00:22:16,599 --> 00:22:18,319
[SPEAKER_00] kao je li to onda ok imati doma,

476
00:22:18,319 --> 00:22:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] za ne daj Bože?

477
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:19,220
[SPEAKER_00] Je.

478
00:22:19,220 --> 00:22:20,599
[SPEAKER_00] Oni to imaju doma,

479
00:22:20,599 --> 00:22:21,759
[SPEAKER_01] kao i oni ko imaju...

480
00:22:21,759 --> 00:22:23,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mislim za ako se dogodi prvi put,

481
00:22:23,619 --> 00:22:25,140
[SPEAKER_01] to hoću reći.

482
00:22:25,140 --> 00:22:26,700
[SPEAKER_01] Ako se dogodi prvi puta,

483
00:22:26,700 --> 00:22:29,079
[SPEAKER_01] pa ne mogu reći da se rutinski

484
00:22:29,079 --> 00:22:31,779
[SPEAKER_01] ili da ja sad svakom ko se liječi

485
00:22:31,779 --> 00:22:32,940
[SPEAKER_01] kod tebe preporučam,

486
00:22:32,940 --> 00:22:34,119
[SPEAKER_01] evo sad ćemo napisati

487
00:22:34,119 --> 00:22:35,359
[SPEAKER_01] da vi imate klizmicu,

488
00:22:35,359 --> 00:22:36,660
[SPEAKER_01] pa ako bi se desilo.

489
00:22:36,660 --> 00:22:39,420
[SPEAKER_01] Možda bi to razgovarala sa onima

490
00:22:39,420 --> 00:22:41,400
[SPEAKER_01] koji imaju jako opterećujuću

491
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:42,579
[SPEAKER_01] obiteljsku anamnezu,

492
00:22:42,579 --> 00:22:43,720
[SPEAKER_01] pa da imaju sad, ne znam,

493
00:22:43,720 --> 00:22:44,900
[SPEAKER_01] da je ovo treće dijete,

494
00:22:44,900 --> 00:22:46,500
[SPEAKER_01] da im je dvoje imalo tako

495
00:22:46,500 --> 00:22:48,599
[SPEAKER_01] i da oni su već super iskusni,

496
00:22:48,599 --> 00:22:51,380
[SPEAKER_01] pa sigurno neće bez veze to primijeniti.

497
00:22:51,380 --> 00:22:53,339
[SPEAKER_01] Jer, recimo, koja je situacija

498
00:22:53,339 --> 00:22:54,799
[SPEAKER_01] koja može podsjećati

499
00:22:54,799 --> 00:22:56,259
[SPEAKER_01] na febrilne konvulzije,

500
00:22:56,259 --> 00:22:57,359
[SPEAKER_01] a nije,

501
00:22:57,359 --> 00:22:59,299
[SPEAKER_01] to je situacija kada imamo

502
00:22:59,299 --> 00:23:01,480
[SPEAKER_01] nagli porast temperature,

503
00:23:01,779 --> 00:23:03,359
[SPEAKER_01] u bakterijskim infekcijama.

504
00:23:03,359 --> 00:23:04,940
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to je tresavica

505
00:23:04,940 --> 00:23:06,619
[SPEAKER_01] i periferna cijanoza.

506
00:23:06,619 --> 00:23:09,539
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, dijete kod naglog poraste temperature,

507
00:23:09,539 --> 00:23:12,799
[SPEAKER_01] znači, jako tresa ekstremitetima

508
00:23:12,799 --> 00:23:14,039
[SPEAKER_01] i rukama i nogama,

509
00:23:14,039 --> 00:23:17,119
[SPEAKER_01] često ima plave vrškove prstića,

510
00:23:17,119 --> 00:23:17,839
[SPEAKER_01] usnice,

511
00:23:17,839 --> 00:23:19,559
[SPEAKER_01] to se najčešće dešava,

512
00:23:19,559 --> 00:23:22,640
[SPEAKER_01] recimo, kod akutne urinarne infekcije,

513
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:23,619
[SPEAKER_01] kod malih beba.

514
00:23:23,839 --> 00:23:24,400
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to je znak...

515
00:23:24,400 --> 00:23:24,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo što ste spominjali,

516
00:23:24,599 --> 00:23:25,619
[SPEAKER_00] cijanoza, što je to?

517
00:23:25,619 --> 00:23:27,700
[SPEAKER_01] Cijanoza je plavičasta boja.

518
00:23:27,700 --> 00:23:30,279
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, zato što se jako žilice stisnu.

519
00:23:30,279 --> 00:23:33,559
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to je znak često prodora bakterije u krv.

520
00:23:33,559 --> 00:23:35,339
[SPEAKER_01] Kad imate, kad nekog pitate

521
00:23:35,339 --> 00:23:36,500
[SPEAKER_01] kakva je temperatura,

522
00:23:36,500 --> 00:23:37,500
[SPEAKER_01] pa je visoka,

523
00:23:37,500 --> 00:23:39,640
[SPEAKER_01] pa da li u tu temperaturu dijete

524
00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:41,440
[SPEAKER_01] ima neku tresavicu.

525
00:23:41,440 --> 00:23:43,500
[SPEAKER_01] Čimo nema, ajmo reći,

526
00:23:43,500 --> 00:23:45,299
[SPEAKER_01] možda je manja šansa

527
00:23:45,299 --> 00:23:46,700
[SPEAKER_01] da je neka ozbiljnija bolest.

528
00:23:46,700 --> 00:23:47,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kad neko vam dođe,

529
00:23:47,980 --> 00:23:49,880
[SPEAKER_01] ima temperature koje su praćene

530
00:23:49,880 --> 00:23:52,400
[SPEAKER_01] tresavicom i nekako lošim stanjem,

531
00:23:52,579 --> 00:23:54,539
[SPEAKER_01] to je obično češće znak

532
00:23:54,539 --> 00:23:56,519
[SPEAKER_01] za neku bakterijsku bolest.

533
00:23:56,519 --> 00:24:01,519
[SPEAKER_00] A ona klasična zimica, groznica?

534
00:24:01,519 --> 00:24:02,799
[SPEAKER_00] Zimica je to.

535
00:24:02,799 --> 00:24:03,940
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, kako da to razlikujem?

536
00:24:03,940 --> 00:24:06,339
[SPEAKER_01] To je to, ali recimo tresavica je malo dramatičnija.

537
00:24:06,339 --> 00:24:09,599
[SPEAKER_01] Tresavica, nekad ljudi kad i dolaze u hitnu,

538
00:24:09,599 --> 00:24:11,599
[SPEAKER_01] znači ti prosto kad ti daju

539
00:24:11,599 --> 00:24:12,920
[SPEAKER_01] anamnestičke podatke,

540
00:24:12,920 --> 00:24:14,720
[SPEAKER_01] iskreno ne možeš biti siguran

541
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:18,140
[SPEAKER_01] da li su to bile febrilne konvulzije,

542
00:24:18,140 --> 00:24:20,700
[SPEAKER_01] to je ti jednostavni motorički napade

543
00:24:20,700 --> 00:24:21,779
[SPEAKER_01] u temperaturi,

544
00:24:21,779 --> 00:24:22,559
[SPEAKER_01] jako je visoko,

545
00:24:22,559 --> 00:24:23,799
[SPEAKER_01] jer oni se ni ne snađu,

546
00:24:23,799 --> 00:24:25,099
[SPEAKER_01] oni jadni kad je prvi puta

547
00:24:25,099 --> 00:24:27,359
[SPEAKER_01] dođu u visoko febrilni,

548
00:24:27,359 --> 00:24:28,539
[SPEAKER_01] tako u hitnu službu,

549
00:24:28,539 --> 00:24:29,779
[SPEAKER_01] jer nisu se niti snaži

550
00:24:29,779 --> 00:24:31,019
[SPEAKER_01] da bi skidili temperaturu,

551
00:24:31,019 --> 00:24:31,599
[SPEAKER_01] niti gledali,

552
00:24:31,599 --> 00:24:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] zato što ono što sam rekla,

553
00:24:33,000 --> 00:24:34,740
[SPEAKER_01] to izgleda stvarno dramatično.

554
00:24:34,740 --> 00:24:39,359
[SPEAKER_01] i ko je doživio nije mu ovoga jednostavno.

555
00:24:39,359 --> 00:24:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] A je li to, može biti opasno?

556
00:24:40,920 --> 00:24:41,960
[SPEAKER_00] Što?

557
00:24:41,960 --> 00:24:44,440
[SPEAKER_00] Pardon, febrilne konvulzije,

558
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:45,339
[SPEAKER_00] sad o tom razmišljam.

559
00:24:45,339 --> 00:24:48,380
[SPEAKER_01] U principu, febrilne konvulzije,

560
00:24:48,380 --> 00:24:50,740
[SPEAKER_01] ako su jednostavne i praćene,

561
00:24:50,740 --> 00:24:52,900
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo uslijed neke virusne bolesti,

562
00:24:52,900 --> 00:24:55,039
[SPEAKER_01] ne jel spontano prestaju,

563
00:24:55,539 --> 00:24:57,559
[SPEAKER_01] ali ako febrilne konvulzije,

564
00:24:57,559 --> 00:24:59,359
[SPEAKER_01] takve, znači djeti ima temperaturu

565
00:24:59,359 --> 00:25:00,720
[SPEAKER_01] i napad se ne smiruje

566
00:25:00,720 --> 00:25:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] i da su dali klizmu

567
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:03,160
[SPEAKER_01] ili da damo bukolan,

568
00:25:03,160 --> 00:25:04,700
[SPEAKER_01] znam či mi uvijek moramo

569
00:25:04,700 --> 00:25:06,359
[SPEAKER_01] se javiti u bolnicu

570
00:25:06,359 --> 00:25:07,299
[SPEAKER_01] kad je tako stanje,

571
00:25:07,299 --> 00:25:08,359
[SPEAKER_01] jer febrilne konvulzije

572
00:25:08,359 --> 00:25:10,420
[SPEAKER_01] vam mogu biti znak i meningitisa.

573
00:25:10,420 --> 00:25:12,660
[SPEAKER_01] Znači dok se sve ne poanalizira,

574
00:25:12,660 --> 00:25:15,140
[SPEAKER_01] ima djete neku infekciju

575
00:25:15,140 --> 00:25:16,200
[SPEAKER_01] sa temperaturom,

576
00:25:16,200 --> 00:25:17,759
[SPEAKER_01] izvade nalaze i ne vidi

577
00:25:17,759 --> 00:25:20,339
[SPEAKER_01] i zaustavi ako se nije odmah napad u bolnici,

578
00:25:20,339 --> 00:25:22,960
[SPEAKER_01] onda nekad je potrebno i analizirati

579
00:25:22,960 --> 00:25:24,460
[SPEAKER_01] da li je zahvaćen sa bolesti

580
00:25:24,460 --> 00:25:26,119
[SPEAKER_01] središnji živčani sustav.

581
00:25:26,119 --> 00:25:28,819
[SPEAKER_01] Najčešće su bezazlene.

582
00:25:28,819 --> 00:25:30,980
[SPEAKER_01] Uslijet neke virusne bolesti

583
00:25:30,980 --> 00:25:33,119
[SPEAKER_01] zbog prepodražljivosti neurona

584
00:25:33,119 --> 00:25:35,480
[SPEAKER_01] traju kratko i spontano

585
00:25:35,480 --> 00:25:37,359
[SPEAKER_01] dok se ti ni ne snađeš prođu.

586
00:25:37,359 --> 00:25:39,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo sad, sad ću promijeniti

587
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:41,559
[SPEAKER_00] malo temu samo da se opustim.

588
00:25:41,559 --> 00:25:44,180
[SPEAKER_00] A to je ono što sam doživjela

589
00:25:44,180 --> 00:25:46,400
[SPEAKER_00] sto puta i vjerojatno svaka mama,

590
00:25:46,400 --> 00:25:49,799
[SPEAKER_00] a to su ozljede malo gdjeteta

591
00:25:49,799 --> 00:25:51,480
[SPEAKER_00] ne na radu nego u igri.

592
00:25:52,619 --> 00:25:54,859
[SPEAKER_00] A prvo vjerojatno to doživimo

593
00:25:54,859 --> 00:25:56,299
[SPEAKER_00] kad nam beba padne s kreveta.

594
00:25:56,299 --> 00:25:58,140
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

595
00:25:58,140 --> 00:25:59,880
[SPEAKER_00] Jesam li u pravu?

596
00:25:59,880 --> 00:26:00,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ili je to samo moj sučaj?

597
00:26:00,900 --> 00:26:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste, jeste.

598
00:26:01,380 --> 00:26:03,720
[SPEAKER_00] I što kad mala beba, ono, nismo ni skužili,

599
00:26:03,720 --> 00:26:05,359
[SPEAKER_00] ona se ipak zna okretati,

600
00:26:05,359 --> 00:26:06,740
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu je sam tako ostaviti,

601
00:26:06,740 --> 00:26:08,319
[SPEAKER_00] ono možda je mentalno jedan jasučić.

602
00:26:09,039 --> 00:26:10,819
[SPEAKER_00] I to se obično dogodi kad, ne znam,

603
00:26:10,819 --> 00:26:12,980
[SPEAKER_00] ni ne okreneš se, beba padne,

604
00:26:12,980 --> 00:26:15,319
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo ako ti je prvo dijete.

605
00:26:15,319 --> 00:26:18,920
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, meni je to bilo ono strašno, strašno, strašno iskustvo.

606
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:20,480
[SPEAKER_00] Sad se malo smijem samo i sebi.

607
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:22,440
[SPEAKER_00] Čak mi je žao što sam insistirala

608
00:26:22,440 --> 00:26:24,680
[SPEAKER_00] da ga vodimo na hitnu,

609
00:26:24,680 --> 00:26:26,319
[SPEAKER_00] pa smo mu tamo i slikali glavu.

610
00:26:26,319 --> 00:26:27,680
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da je to bilo možda nepotrebno,

611
00:26:27,779 --> 00:26:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] ali, dobro, na prvom dijete tu se učimo.

612
00:26:30,559 --> 00:26:34,240
[SPEAKER_00] Što kad dijete padne?

613
00:26:34,240 --> 00:26:36,180
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, recimo, kad beba padne s kreveta,

614
00:26:36,180 --> 00:26:40,799
[SPEAKER_00] je li to, ono, ma ništa svakome se dogodi

615
00:26:40,799 --> 00:26:42,740
[SPEAKER_00] ili ipak treba odvesti dijete na hitnu?

616
00:26:42,740 --> 00:26:45,420
[SPEAKER_00] I ono kad kažu prati dijete,

617
00:26:45,420 --> 00:26:47,960
[SPEAKER_00] što uopće znači ako ti je to prvo dijete?

618
00:26:47,960 --> 00:26:49,200
[SPEAKER_00] Što znači pratiti dijete?

619
00:26:49,200 --> 00:26:50,920
[SPEAKER_01] Na, na, pa ovako.

620
00:26:50,920 --> 00:26:53,779
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo, pa dosta je bitno i sa koje visine pada,

621
00:26:53,779 --> 00:26:56,160
[SPEAKER_01] jer danas znamo da nisu svi kreveti niski,

622
00:26:56,160 --> 00:26:58,519
[SPEAKER_01] danas je u modi imati visoki krevet,

623
00:26:58,519 --> 00:27:01,420
[SPEAKER_01] znači nije baš mala visina, možda i metar,

624
00:27:01,420 --> 00:27:04,619
[SPEAKER_01] zavisi da li nam je dolje neki debeli tepih

625
00:27:04,619 --> 00:27:05,960
[SPEAKER_01] ili kako je palo,

626
00:27:05,960 --> 00:27:08,940
[SPEAKER_01] da li možda ako se prevalilo preko jastuka na jastuk,

627
00:27:08,940 --> 00:27:11,180
[SPEAKER_01] da li je udarilo glavom u parket,

628
00:27:11,180 --> 00:27:13,160
[SPEAKER_01] na koji način je palo,

629
00:27:13,160 --> 00:27:14,799
[SPEAKER_01] da li ste vi to vidjeli uopće

630
00:27:14,799 --> 00:27:17,519
[SPEAKER_01] i onda kasnije kako se dijete ponaša.

631
00:27:17,519 --> 00:27:19,680
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno da se čovjek preplaši,

632
00:27:19,680 --> 00:27:22,799
[SPEAKER_01] ali tu samo bi istaknula da molim sve,

633
00:27:22,799 --> 00:27:25,299
[SPEAKER_01] da se beba nikada ne ostavlja

634
00:27:25,299 --> 00:27:26,920
[SPEAKER_01] bez da se drži lagano,

635
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] pridržava rukom.

636
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:29,779
[SPEAKER_01] Pa čak i dok je presvlačimo,

637
00:27:29,779 --> 00:27:31,039
[SPEAKER_01] još se ne okreće.

638
00:27:31,039 --> 00:27:32,460
[SPEAKER_01] Samo da se okrenemo,

639
00:27:32,460 --> 00:27:34,059
[SPEAKER_01] da kao dohvatimo si ručnik.

640
00:27:34,059 --> 00:27:35,920
[SPEAKER_01] To je, ma niti sekunda.

641
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:39,779
[SPEAKER_01] Jer postoji jedan dan će se beba prvi puta okrenuti.

642
00:27:40,660 --> 00:27:42,039
[SPEAKER_01] A vi ne znate kad je taj dan.

643
00:27:42,039 --> 00:27:44,359
[SPEAKER_01] Da li će to biti taj dan da se to ne dobodi?

644
00:27:44,359 --> 00:27:45,160
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ga pamtim.

645
00:27:45,160 --> 00:27:47,700
[SPEAKER_01] To je uvijek onako, to nikad nije.

646
00:27:47,700 --> 00:27:50,500
[SPEAKER_01] Sad sam ja ostavio beba puže pa je pala s visine.

647
00:27:50,500 --> 00:27:54,119
[SPEAKER_01] To je najčešće kod još manjih koji se uopće ne gibaju,

648
00:27:54,119 --> 00:27:59,660
[SPEAKER_01] ali ipak imaju neke pokrete kojima oni dođu i pomaknu se i padnu.

649
00:28:00,319 --> 00:28:04,599
[SPEAKER_01] E sada, ako je to nekako da je beba odna počela plakati,

650
00:28:04,599 --> 00:28:06,500
[SPEAKER_01] nije plakala dugo,

651
00:28:06,500 --> 00:28:08,220
[SPEAKER_01] ponaša se normalno,

652
00:28:08,220 --> 00:28:10,180
[SPEAKER_01] nije povraćala nakon toga,

653
00:28:10,180 --> 00:28:12,079
[SPEAKER_01] bila je plačljiva,

654
00:28:12,079 --> 00:28:15,059
[SPEAKER_01] ali taj plač nije da traje sad satima,

655
00:28:15,059 --> 00:28:16,819
[SPEAKER_01] pa da vam odbija hranu,

656
00:28:16,819 --> 00:28:19,299
[SPEAKER_01] da vam izgleda totalno nezainteresirana.

657
00:28:19,299 --> 00:28:22,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ako beba se već igra, sad vi dođete i tako,

658
00:28:22,680 --> 00:28:28,339
[SPEAKER_01] onda bi svakako to bi mogli biti neki početni znaci potresa mozga

659
00:28:28,339 --> 00:28:32,660
[SPEAKER_01] kod male bebe i to bi da se ipak javite ovoga.

660
00:28:32,660 --> 00:28:35,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ako je tako nešto da je dramatično,

661
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:37,880
[SPEAKER_01] da nije prošlo, ne znam, za pet minuta je zaplakala

662
00:28:37,880 --> 00:28:39,079
[SPEAKER_01] i sve drugo normalno,

663
00:28:39,079 --> 00:28:40,400
[SPEAKER_01] onda možda i ne bi.

664
00:28:40,400 --> 00:28:43,920
[SPEAKER_01] I da nije neka velika, ne znam, čvoruga izašla.

665
00:28:43,920 --> 00:28:44,460
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

666
00:28:44,460 --> 00:28:47,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ali isto, bebine kosti su možda malo mekanije.

667
00:28:47,799 --> 00:28:51,700
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, ovisno pod kojem kutem pada i na šta tvrdo,

668
00:28:51,700 --> 00:28:53,599
[SPEAKER_01] može doći i do frakture,

669
00:28:53,599 --> 00:28:55,839
[SPEAKER_01] koje vi možete vidjeti kraniogramom.

670
00:28:55,839 --> 00:28:57,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, naravno vi ono ste rekli,

671
00:28:58,180 --> 00:29:00,019
[SPEAKER_01] možda nisam trebala, to je uvijek lako.

672
00:29:00,019 --> 00:29:03,299
[SPEAKER_01] Znate, vi sad u panici reći kad sve prođe, kad je sve dobro.

673
00:29:03,299 --> 00:29:05,880
[SPEAKER_00] Da, mislim, u mom slučaju stvarno je i nisko krevet,

674
00:29:05,880 --> 00:29:11,059
[SPEAKER_00] i debeli je, tepih i nekako duboko u sebi znam da nije ništa strašno,

675
00:29:11,059 --> 00:29:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] ali meni je iskreno više trebala kao friškoj mami

676
00:29:13,940 --> 00:29:15,680
[SPEAKER_00] još pod tim hormonima i sve.

677
00:29:15,680 --> 00:29:17,079
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je više trebalo da mi neko kaže

678
00:29:17,079 --> 00:29:18,720
[SPEAKER_00] sve je ok, nijemo ništa.

679
00:29:18,720 --> 00:29:20,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ono da stavi pečat na to.

680
00:29:20,180 --> 00:29:24,339
[SPEAKER_00] Onda se nekad pitam je li vrijedilo toga da ga izlažem tom zračenju i sve,

681
00:29:24,480 --> 00:29:28,779
[SPEAKER_00] ali ok, nekad mami treba da liječni kaže sve ok.

682
00:29:28,779 --> 00:29:31,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ali tu mislim da bi bilo, naravno da nije uvijek moguće,

683
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:35,440
[SPEAKER_01] čak i srednoći, neki vaš kontakt sa pediatrem,

684
00:29:35,440 --> 00:29:38,640
[SPEAKER_01] vašim, u kojeg imate povjerenja,

685
00:29:38,640 --> 00:29:40,819
[SPEAKER_01] s kojim možete to prokomentirati,

686
00:29:40,819 --> 00:29:43,359
[SPEAKER_01] pa ako je dan, ne znam, hitno desilo se palo,

687
00:29:43,359 --> 00:29:46,339
[SPEAKER_01] možda pedijata radi, ali barem mail, nešto, nešto,

688
00:29:46,339 --> 00:29:49,859
[SPEAKER_01] da vi imate ili nekako da s njim općenito pričate

689
00:29:49,859 --> 00:29:51,119
[SPEAKER_01] o tak nekim pitanjima.

690
00:29:51,119 --> 00:29:54,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ako mi se desi, je li to na jednom sistemarskom

691
00:29:54,519 --> 00:29:56,160
[SPEAKER_01] koji se rade, koji su redoviti,

692
00:29:56,160 --> 00:30:00,339
[SPEAKER_01] bi trebalo biti vrijeme kada vi postavljate ta neka svoja pitanja

693
00:30:00,339 --> 00:30:03,119
[SPEAKER_01] i možda drugi puta ne bi otišla.

694
00:30:03,119 --> 00:30:05,460
[SPEAKER_01] To je sa drugim djetetom sigurno ne bi.

695
00:30:05,460 --> 00:30:10,200
[SPEAKER_01] Ali recimo, ako djete bi plakalo jako dugo

696
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:12,960
[SPEAKER_01] i pokazuje te znakove, ako je to malo dojenče,

697
00:30:13,420 --> 00:30:17,319
[SPEAKER_01] da neće uopće jesti, da je drugačije vama,

698
00:30:17,319 --> 00:30:20,099
[SPEAKER_01] ili da je pospano, da samo se uspava.

699
00:30:20,099 --> 00:30:22,099
[SPEAKER_01] Vi očekujete, treba bi biti period, ne znam,

700
00:30:22,099 --> 00:30:24,359
[SPEAKER_01] sad bi trebalo biti djete gladno i igrat se,

701
00:30:24,359 --> 00:30:28,079
[SPEAKER_01] onda bi svakako da odete, bez obzira što znamo

702
00:30:28,079 --> 00:30:31,359
[SPEAKER_01] da potres mozga, ako nema nikakve frakture

703
00:30:31,359 --> 00:30:34,019
[SPEAKER_01] i to se ne liječi, on spontano prolazi.

704
00:30:34,019 --> 00:30:37,259
[SPEAKER_01] A ako je djete veće, recimo da već hoda

705
00:30:37,259 --> 00:30:40,359
[SPEAKER_01] i palo je vrlo nezgodno, obično na potiljak,

706
00:30:40,359 --> 00:30:43,420
[SPEAKER_01] da li je to udarilo glavom nezgodno

707
00:30:43,420 --> 00:30:46,940
[SPEAKER_01] i nakon toga uz jaki plać je povraćalo.

708
00:30:46,940 --> 00:30:50,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ili onda vidite da je teturavo u hodu

709
00:30:50,079 --> 00:30:52,599
[SPEAKER_01] ili je jako razdražljivo, plačljivo

710
00:30:52,599 --> 00:30:55,019
[SPEAKER_01] ili primjećujete da postoje,

711
00:30:55,019 --> 00:30:57,220
[SPEAKER_01] ali to su već ozvidne ozljede razlike

712
00:30:57,220 --> 00:31:00,720
[SPEAKER_01] u zjenicama, onda je to zapravo alarm

713
00:31:00,720 --> 00:31:03,059
[SPEAKER_01] za hitno javiti se u bolnicu.

714
00:31:03,059 --> 00:31:06,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, ajme, htjela sam neku laganu temu,

715
00:31:06,480 --> 00:31:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] a sad ste me opet nasekirali, imam jednog,

716
00:31:10,539 --> 00:31:13,460
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj drugi, jedne se su druga djeca uvijek živahnija,

717
00:31:13,460 --> 00:31:16,740
[SPEAKER_00] barem mi se čini često bude slučaj

718
00:31:16,740 --> 00:31:21,599
[SPEAKER_00] i on jadan već, već zna kad se udari

719
00:31:21,599 --> 00:31:24,599
[SPEAKER_00] i onda vidiče led, led i onda sam otvara

720
00:31:24,599 --> 00:31:27,359
[SPEAKER_00] onu policu u hladnja koju uzima led i stavlja

721
00:31:27,359 --> 00:31:30,640
[SPEAKER_00] i za pet minuta opet trči kao da...

722
00:31:30,640 --> 00:31:31,160
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

723
00:31:31,160 --> 00:31:35,180
[SPEAKER_01] Kao da nema taj strah od potencijalnog udarca.

724
00:31:35,180 --> 00:31:37,299
[SPEAKER_01] Ali vi ste sigurno drugačiji.

725
00:31:37,299 --> 00:31:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači vi ste opušteni i vi sad znate

726
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:41,720
[SPEAKER_01] da tako i dijete to osjeti

727
00:31:41,720 --> 00:31:43,440
[SPEAKER_01] i najčešće su tebe zazlene

728
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:45,779
[SPEAKER_01] kad se udari i da izađe čvorga

729
00:31:45,779 --> 00:31:48,539
[SPEAKER_01] koja odmah izleti da je centimetar dva,

730
00:31:48,539 --> 00:31:50,680
[SPEAKER_01] onako, ko u crtiću, kak se kaže,

731
00:31:50,680 --> 00:31:53,200
[SPEAKER_01] i da je plavo led i bit će dobro.

732
00:31:53,599 --> 00:31:55,759
[SPEAKER_01] Više je ono, ako padne na potiljak,

733
00:31:55,759 --> 00:31:58,980
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, bez gubitka svijesti.

734
00:31:58,980 --> 00:32:01,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ako izgubi svijest, onda molim vas odmah o to.

735
00:32:01,400 --> 00:32:03,339
[SPEAKER_01] Ili ako ono povraća i tako.

736
00:32:03,339 --> 00:32:06,180
[SPEAKER_01] Ali najčešće su to bezazleni padovi

737
00:32:06,180 --> 00:32:07,319
[SPEAKER_01] i stvarno ne treba.

738
00:32:07,319 --> 00:32:09,460
[SPEAKER_01] Dijete kad prohodava padne,

739
00:32:09,460 --> 00:32:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali ako odete u hitnu,

740
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:13,200
[SPEAKER_01] tamo kad dođete, onda jednostavno

741
00:32:13,200 --> 00:32:15,480
[SPEAKER_01] neko mora vidjeti da li je sve u redu,

742
00:32:15,480 --> 00:32:17,740
[SPEAKER_01] da se ne desi da ono do dvije godine

743
00:32:17,740 --> 00:32:19,960
[SPEAKER_01] bili ste, ne znam, deset puta

744
00:32:19,960 --> 00:32:21,960
[SPEAKER_01] i šest puta je kranjogram radio

745
00:32:21,960 --> 00:32:22,960
[SPEAKER_01] i bilo uvek uredno.

746
00:32:23,599 --> 00:32:26,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ali vi svakako ovoga,

747
00:32:26,519 --> 00:32:28,319
[SPEAKER_01] vidi se čim ste opušteni

748
00:32:28,319 --> 00:32:29,460
[SPEAKER_01] i kad je drugo dijete,

749
00:32:29,460 --> 00:32:32,279
[SPEAKER_01] znate prepoznat kao roditelj

750
00:32:32,279 --> 00:32:35,140
[SPEAKER_01] da nešto nije potrebno ići na hitnu

751
00:32:35,140 --> 00:32:36,119
[SPEAKER_01] ili da nije ozbiljno.

752
00:32:36,119 --> 00:32:38,160
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ma, i nemam izbora

753
00:32:38,160 --> 00:32:39,619
[SPEAKER_00] nego biti opuštenija,

754
00:32:39,619 --> 00:32:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] jer inače bi bila konstantno na hitnoj.

755
00:32:42,579 --> 00:32:44,140
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, jednostavno,

756
00:32:44,140 --> 00:32:45,759
[SPEAKER_00] tako je dijete da...

757
00:32:45,759 --> 00:32:48,680
[SPEAKER_00] živahanje, živahanje i nema osjećaj...

758
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:52,559
[SPEAKER_00] Nema strah ni od granica,

759
00:32:52,559 --> 00:32:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] ni od potencijalnog udarca,

760
00:32:54,380 --> 00:32:55,680
[SPEAKER_00] za razliku od ovog drugog,

761
00:32:55,680 --> 00:32:59,779
[SPEAKER_00] koji, ako je granica, ne znam,

762
00:32:59,779 --> 00:33:01,279
[SPEAKER_00] nemoj ići preko nečega,

763
00:33:01,279 --> 00:33:02,839
[SPEAKER_00] ono neće ni blizu tog nečega.

764
00:33:02,839 --> 00:33:04,259
[SPEAKER_00] Jednostavno različita djeca.

765
00:33:05,480 --> 00:33:08,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj drugi me prisilio da se opustim

766
00:33:08,599 --> 00:33:11,160
[SPEAKER_00] i evo, opustila sam se.

767
00:33:11,160 --> 00:33:15,480
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala sam ospitati još u vezi

768
00:33:15,480 --> 00:33:17,759
[SPEAKER_00] treće jedne stvari,

769
00:33:17,759 --> 00:33:19,160
[SPEAKER_00] a to je osip.

770
00:33:19,160 --> 00:33:24,559
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono nešto što ne volimo vidjeti,

771
00:33:24,559 --> 00:33:26,859
[SPEAKER_00] kako to kad ne znamo što je sad to,

772
00:33:26,859 --> 00:33:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] od kad, kad se to pojavilo,

773
00:33:29,380 --> 00:33:32,119
[SPEAKER_00] onda još kad dođemo kod pediatra,

774
00:33:32,119 --> 00:33:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] pa mama, kada ste to primijetili,

775
00:33:34,079 --> 00:33:36,400
[SPEAKER_00] a sad ono, pa ne znam točno,

776
00:33:36,400 --> 00:33:38,240
[SPEAKER_00] kao da se odjednom samo pojavilo to nešto.

777
00:33:38,240 --> 00:33:41,880
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu hvala da sad je uvijek bilo

778
00:33:41,880 --> 00:33:44,420
[SPEAKER_00] ili nakon, šta je ono nečeći,

779
00:33:44,420 --> 00:33:45,759
[SPEAKER_00] nakon temperature isto,

780
00:33:45,759 --> 00:33:51,279
[SPEAKER_00] ili ona bolest šaka usta stopala.

781
00:33:51,279 --> 00:33:55,700
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je bilo u okviru nekih normalnih dječjih bolesti.

782
00:33:55,700 --> 00:33:57,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ali evo, općenito,

783
00:33:57,859 --> 00:34:01,059
[SPEAKER_00] recimo da prvi put vidim nekakav osip,

784
00:34:01,059 --> 00:34:02,059
[SPEAKER_00] djete tu po koži,

785
00:34:02,059 --> 00:34:03,319
[SPEAKER_00] što napraviti?

786
00:34:03,400 --> 00:34:06,240
[SPEAKER_00] Isto, je li to alarm za otići liječniku

787
00:34:06,240 --> 00:34:08,699
[SPEAKER_00] ili ne mora biti, koliko god neka družno djeluje?

788
00:34:08,699 --> 00:34:12,719
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, osipi su kod djece jako česti.

789
00:34:12,719 --> 00:34:15,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, s jedne strane imamo osipe

790
00:34:15,079 --> 00:34:17,579
[SPEAKER_01] u sklopu nekih infekcija, bolesti,

791
00:34:17,579 --> 00:34:19,559
[SPEAKER_01] različitih virusnih bolesti

792
00:34:19,559 --> 00:34:23,059
[SPEAKER_01] i kod djece jako često prati osip.

793
00:34:23,239 --> 00:34:25,059
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ovo što ste mi naveli,

794
00:34:25,059 --> 00:34:27,739
[SPEAKER_01] postoje osipi koji su tipični,

795
00:34:27,739 --> 00:34:30,840
[SPEAKER_01] kao što su recimo kod bolesti usta, šaka, stopala

796
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] ili kod kozica.

797
00:34:32,000 --> 00:34:33,659
[SPEAKER_01] To su nam mihurići.

798
00:34:33,659 --> 00:34:35,300
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, prvo kao mali prištići,

799
00:34:35,300 --> 00:34:37,539
[SPEAKER_01] pretvoje su vodini mihurić, pa pucaju.

800
00:34:37,539 --> 00:34:41,300
[SPEAKER_01] Onda imamo osipe koji su u razini kože,

801
00:34:41,300 --> 00:34:43,380
[SPEAKER_01] ružičasti, veći, manji.

802
00:34:43,760 --> 00:34:45,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ako oni bljede na pritisak

803
00:34:45,460 --> 00:34:47,139
[SPEAKER_01] i dijete je dobrog općeg stanja.

804
00:34:47,139 --> 00:34:49,980
[SPEAKER_01] Bljede na pritisak znači kad vi pretisnete sa brstom

805
00:34:49,980 --> 00:34:51,860
[SPEAKER_01] da zapravo nestane i onda se vrati.

806
00:34:51,860 --> 00:34:54,599
[SPEAKER_01] I uz to kad je dijete dobrog općeg stanja,

807
00:34:54,599 --> 00:34:57,179
[SPEAKER_01] to je najčešće bezazlen osip

808
00:34:57,179 --> 00:35:00,940
[SPEAKER_01] koji se javlja uslijed različitih enteroviroza kod djece.

809
00:35:00,940 --> 00:35:04,039
[SPEAKER_01] Isto tako imate, ne znam, tipične bolesti,

810
00:35:04,039 --> 00:35:06,780
[SPEAKER_01] ono što je često imate u epidemijama,

811
00:35:06,780 --> 00:35:08,780
[SPEAKER_01] ono što pričaju mame, pa je to,

812
00:35:08,780 --> 00:35:11,039
[SPEAKER_01] joj, jel dijete ima petu bolest,

813
00:35:11,039 --> 00:35:13,400
[SPEAKER_01] pa je to ono što su obrazi kao jako rumeni,

814
00:35:13,400 --> 00:35:15,840
[SPEAKER_01] kao da je neko iz pljuskao obraze izgleda,

815
00:35:15,840 --> 00:35:20,659
[SPEAKER_01] a šaroliki kao jedna mrežica ili čipka po tijelu,

816
00:35:20,659 --> 00:35:23,219
[SPEAKER_01] taj osip nije opasan.

817
00:35:23,219 --> 00:35:26,059
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, on je u sklopu tog virusa i prolazi.

818
00:35:26,059 --> 00:35:28,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ili ovo što ste rekli, nakon temperature,

819
00:35:28,639 --> 00:35:30,579
[SPEAKER_01] to je ono, ne znam, da li postoje dijete

820
00:35:30,579 --> 00:35:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] koje nije prebolo u narodu poznatu trodnevnu vručicu,

821
00:35:33,800 --> 00:35:38,559
[SPEAKER_01] ne, i ovoga, znači, dijete ima veliku temperaturu,

822
00:35:38,559 --> 00:35:42,099
[SPEAKER_01] ništa ne vidiš tu, smo pametni te kad temperatura prođe,

823
00:35:42,179 --> 00:35:45,360
[SPEAKER_01] se onda pojavi osip, mrljasti krene od glave,

824
00:35:45,360 --> 00:35:49,039
[SPEAKER_01] ispušta se dolje i nekad izgleda onako zastrašujuće,

825
00:35:49,039 --> 00:35:51,199
[SPEAKER_01] ali je to cijelo u osipu ružičastom.

826
00:35:51,199 --> 00:35:53,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ali taj osip nije opasan,

827
00:35:53,400 --> 00:35:55,619
[SPEAKER_01] jer blijedi na pritisak,

828
00:35:55,619 --> 00:35:56,960
[SPEAKER_01] dijete je super stanja,

829
00:35:56,960 --> 00:36:00,099
[SPEAKER_01] tako da u principu se ne bi trebali brinuti.

830
00:36:00,219 --> 00:36:04,099
[SPEAKER_01] ili ako primijetimo u temperaturi malo da se zacrveni dijete,

831
00:36:04,099 --> 00:36:07,639
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda nestane, znači, to su osjetljive kože,

832
00:36:07,639 --> 00:36:09,400
[SPEAKER_01] pa se zna dogoditi.

833
00:36:09,400 --> 00:36:11,500
[SPEAKER_01] Imate isto i bakterijske bolesti,

834
00:36:11,500 --> 00:36:13,039
[SPEAKER_01] znači, ono što su epidemije,

835
00:36:13,039 --> 00:36:17,280
[SPEAKER_01] to je osipu sklopu u šarlaha ili skarlatine.

836
00:36:17,400 --> 00:36:21,360
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, čak je to tip osipa koje vi zovete skarlatiniformni,

837
00:36:21,360 --> 00:36:24,400
[SPEAKER_01] znači, usljed nekih virusa se može javiti sličan,

838
00:36:24,400 --> 00:36:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali nas dosta dobro opučuje.

839
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:28,739
[SPEAKER_01] Kada imamo, znači, saznanje da vlada,

840
00:36:28,739 --> 00:36:31,639
[SPEAKER_01] općenito srepto kog da je postoje puno angina

841
00:36:31,639 --> 00:36:34,559
[SPEAKER_01] i onda vidimo anginu, sa ili bez i takav osip,

842
00:36:34,559 --> 00:36:35,460
[SPEAKER_01] to je vrlo sumljivo.

843
00:36:35,460 --> 00:36:37,960
[SPEAKER_01] On je tipičan po trupu, sitno točkasti,

844
00:36:37,960 --> 00:36:41,179
[SPEAKER_01] onda u pazušnim jamama i po ingvinumu.

845
00:36:41,179 --> 00:36:43,760
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, ti osipi nisu opasni.

846
00:36:43,760 --> 00:36:46,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ovaj je za otić doktor ili treba se liječiti antibiotikom.

847
00:36:47,960 --> 00:36:50,280
[SPEAKER_01] Isto tako, ako nisu infekcije,

848
00:36:50,280 --> 00:36:52,519
[SPEAKER_01] dječja koža je jako osjetljiva,

849
00:36:52,519 --> 00:36:54,159
[SPEAKER_01] pogotovo u današnje vrijeme.

850
00:36:54,159 --> 00:36:57,619
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, valda, 50% djece ima suhu, osjetljivu,

851
00:36:57,619 --> 00:37:00,480
[SPEAKER_01] perutavu kožu ili imaju negdje na mjestima

852
00:37:00,480 --> 00:37:03,019
[SPEAKER_01] hrapavost koja može biti malo više

853
00:37:03,019 --> 00:37:05,400
[SPEAKER_01] ili malo manje crvena, što zovemo u narodu,

854
00:37:05,400 --> 00:37:07,139
[SPEAKER_01] kao i mališa i či tako.

855
00:37:07,139 --> 00:37:12,199
[SPEAKER_01] To su najčešće razni oblici osjetljive kože,

856
00:37:12,199 --> 00:37:15,199
[SPEAKER_01] se boreje ili tzv. atopijskog dermatitisa,

857
00:37:15,199 --> 00:37:17,340
[SPEAKER_01] koji danas nije rijetkosti,

858
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:19,719
[SPEAKER_01] koji nekad ne izgleda baš lijepo,

859
00:37:19,719 --> 00:37:22,039
[SPEAKER_01] djete svrbi, ali ako je blagi,

860
00:37:22,039 --> 00:37:25,320
[SPEAKER_01] znači tu nema terapijski posebno puno,

861
00:37:25,320 --> 00:37:27,539
[SPEAKER_01] ne radi se odmah silna testiranja,

862
00:37:27,539 --> 00:37:30,059
[SPEAKER_01] nego se primjenjuje emolijentne kreme,

863
00:37:30,059 --> 00:37:33,119
[SPEAKER_01] da se vraća vlaga koži, lipidi,

864
00:37:33,119 --> 00:37:36,079
[SPEAKER_01] pa da manje bilo kakvih alergena može prodreti

865
00:37:36,079 --> 00:37:37,980
[SPEAKER_01] i manje nastaju takve promjene.

866
00:37:37,980 --> 00:37:40,300
[SPEAKER_01] Kad su ozbiljnije, upaljene,

867
00:37:40,300 --> 00:37:44,519
[SPEAKER_01] onda se primjenjuje i specifična terapija tipa kortikosteroida,

868
00:37:44,519 --> 00:37:48,699
[SPEAKER_01] ali to je uvijek dobro u konzultaciji sa dermatologom

869
00:37:48,699 --> 00:37:52,300
[SPEAKER_01] ili ako je to da vidimo da povezujemo da se jako kvari na neku hranu,

870
00:37:52,300 --> 00:37:56,460
[SPEAKER_01] znači u smislu nutritivnih alergija koje se prezentiraju

871
00:37:56,460 --> 00:37:58,820
[SPEAKER_01] kod male djece sa kožnim promjenama,

872
00:37:58,820 --> 00:38:02,400
[SPEAKER_01] onda recimo sa gastroenterologom u konzultaciji

873
00:38:02,400 --> 00:38:04,780
[SPEAKER_01] ne izbaciti sve sami iz hrane i tako

874
00:38:04,780 --> 00:38:09,719
[SPEAKER_01] i svakako terapija posebna za takve kožne promjene.

875
00:38:09,719 --> 00:38:14,920
[SPEAKER_01] E sad to su ti, ajmo reći, neopasni svakodnevni osipi

876
00:38:14,920 --> 00:38:16,500
[SPEAKER_01] s kojima se susrećemo.

877
00:38:16,500 --> 00:38:20,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ili recimo ljeti, ne mogu reći da nije opasan,

878
00:38:20,199 --> 00:38:22,179
[SPEAKER_01] mora se liječiti, jer je zarazan jako.

879
00:38:22,179 --> 00:38:24,840
[SPEAKER_01] To se javlja u epidemijama kod male djece.

880
00:38:24,840 --> 00:38:27,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam da li ste prošli, to je impetigo

881
00:38:27,659 --> 00:38:32,719
[SPEAKER_01] ili stafilodermija, ili zovu se još u narodu slatke kraste.

882
00:38:32,719 --> 00:38:36,639
[SPEAKER_01] Znači to su, kao pojavi se kao jedan prištić

883
00:38:36,639 --> 00:38:40,199
[SPEAKER_01] i onda se napunite kućenicom, kao mi je huri,

884
00:38:40,199 --> 00:38:43,500
[SPEAKER_01] onda pukne i ostane krasta, to se može širit,

885
00:38:43,500 --> 00:38:46,239
[SPEAKER_01] djeca se češkaju i prenose si sama po tijelu.

886
00:38:46,239 --> 00:38:47,659
[SPEAKER_00] Je li najčešće na licu ili?

887
00:38:47,659 --> 00:38:49,659
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo gdje, bilo gdje po koži.

888
00:38:49,780 --> 00:38:52,579
[SPEAKER_01] Znači kada je na licu da ide u nos ili tako u uho,

889
00:38:52,579 --> 00:38:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda obično treba i sistenski antibiotika.

890
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:58,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ovako se lječi sa antibijotskim mastima,

891
00:38:58,340 --> 00:39:01,940
[SPEAKER_01] a širi se najčešće ljeti na moru

892
00:39:01,940 --> 00:39:04,159
[SPEAKER_01] i ovako epidemijski kod dječice.

893
00:39:04,159 --> 00:39:07,900
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, ajmo reći, opasan je zbog toga što se širi.

894
00:39:07,980 --> 00:39:15,539
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo rijetko to sad prodire u krv ili neke ozbiljne da su stvari kod normalno zravog dijeteta.

895
00:39:15,539 --> 00:39:17,780
[SPEAKER_01] A koji je osip opasan?

896
00:39:17,780 --> 00:39:22,039
[SPEAKER_00] Znači ako stisnemo i on onak nestaje, bijelkastije nestaje,

897
00:39:22,039 --> 00:39:24,400
[SPEAKER_00] u principu možemo reći da nije ništa.

898
00:39:24,400 --> 00:39:26,500
[SPEAKER_01] A što ako ne?

899
00:39:26,500 --> 00:39:28,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ostane crveno ili...

900
00:39:28,079 --> 00:39:33,780
[SPEAKER_01] E sada ako ostane, znači opasni osipi su oni koji izgledaju kao krvarenja po koži.

901
00:39:33,780 --> 00:39:38,579
[SPEAKER_01] E sada, to može biti sitno, kao milimetar, to se zove petehija.

902
00:39:38,579 --> 00:39:41,639
[SPEAKER_01] Kad vi stisnete jednu točkicu koja je crvena,

903
00:39:41,639 --> 00:39:44,880
[SPEAKER_01] onako baš crvena kao ili ih ima puno,

904
00:39:44,880 --> 00:39:49,400
[SPEAKER_01] i to ne bljedi, znači to su sitne točkice na bilo kojem djevu tijela,

905
00:39:49,400 --> 00:39:52,639
[SPEAKER_01] to može biti znak ozbiljne bolesti.

906
00:39:52,639 --> 00:39:55,780
[SPEAKER_01] To može biti znak da su trombociti jako niski,

907
00:39:56,139 --> 00:39:58,300
[SPEAKER_01] bilo da je to neka imunološka priča,

908
00:39:58,300 --> 00:39:59,739
[SPEAKER_01] bilo uslijed infekcije,

909
00:39:59,739 --> 00:40:02,280
[SPEAKER_01] a ako su krvarenja veća,

910
00:40:02,280 --> 00:40:03,960
[SPEAKER_01] znači to zovemo ekimoze,

911
00:40:03,960 --> 00:40:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] znači izgledaju kao potkožna krvarenja,

912
00:40:07,000 --> 00:40:08,900
[SPEAKER_01] znači to je ono crveno, veliko.

913
00:40:08,900 --> 00:40:12,760
[SPEAKER_01] To je svakako uz temperaturu alarm

914
00:40:12,760 --> 00:40:17,260
[SPEAKER_01] da se javite ovoga zapravo ne samo čekat svog lječnika,

915
00:40:17,260 --> 00:40:18,099
[SPEAKER_01] nego u bolnicu,

916
00:40:18,099 --> 00:40:20,699
[SPEAKER_01] jer to može biti znak septičnog stanja

917
00:40:20,699 --> 00:40:23,659
[SPEAKER_01] i one ozbiljne bolesti koje se svi bojimo,

918
00:40:23,659 --> 00:40:25,119
[SPEAKER_01] jer je najčešće fatalna,

919
00:40:25,239 --> 00:40:27,019
[SPEAKER_01] to je meningokokna sepse.

920
00:40:27,019 --> 00:40:29,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

921
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:36,320
[SPEAKER_00] Opet ja bježim od ovih teških tema,

922
00:40:36,320 --> 00:40:41,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali zapravo namjeram je bila prebaciti se sad

923
00:40:41,099 --> 00:40:46,059
[SPEAKER_00] na priču o prvim pregledima,

924
00:40:46,860 --> 00:40:49,400
[SPEAKER_00] prve male bebice kad se tek rode,

925
00:40:49,400 --> 00:40:54,019
[SPEAKER_00] kad je najbolje zakazati taj prvi pregled,

926
00:40:54,019 --> 00:40:57,400
[SPEAKER_00] može i prije nego se djete rodi ili nema potrebe,

927
00:40:57,400 --> 00:41:02,880
[SPEAKER_00] i ove kako se zovu posjete patronažnih sestara,

928
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:03,679
[SPEAKER_00] da se tako zovu,

929
00:41:04,639 --> 00:41:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] dajte nam tu neke savijete,

930
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] savijeti su uvijek dobro došli,

931
00:41:08,380 --> 00:41:14,119
[SPEAKER_00] kada otičem prvi pregled i kada kontaktirati patronažnu.

932
00:41:14,840 --> 00:41:16,559
[SPEAKER_00] Prije nego što nastavimo s razgovorom,

933
00:41:16,559 --> 00:41:19,179
[SPEAKER_00] želim zahvaliti sponsoru današnje epizode,

934
00:41:19,179 --> 00:41:20,300
[SPEAKER_00] Mandis Farmu.

935
00:41:20,300 --> 00:41:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] Mandis Farm je

936
00:41:21,460 --> 00:41:23,679
[SPEAKER_00] specializirana prodovaonica lijekova,

937
00:41:23,679 --> 00:41:27,679
[SPEAKER_00] koja spaja dermokozmetičko i nutricionističko savjetovalište,

938
00:41:27,679 --> 00:41:29,800
[SPEAKER_00] nudeći cijelovit pristup zdravlju.

939
00:41:29,800 --> 00:41:33,440
[SPEAKER_00] Uz bogat asortiman vitamina, minerala i dodataka prehrani,

940
00:41:33,440 --> 00:41:37,619
[SPEAKER_00] klijentima pruža besplatne savijete i individualne programe prehrane

941
00:41:37,619 --> 00:41:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] pod stručnim vodstvom nutricionistice Mandis Farma.

942
00:41:41,619 --> 00:41:45,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ali prije svega, to je jedna lijepa obiteljska priča,

943
00:41:45,619 --> 00:41:48,159
[SPEAKER_00] obiteljska tvrtka sa dugom tradicijom

944
00:41:48,159 --> 00:41:53,659
[SPEAKER_00] i istančanim osjećajem za vrijednosti koje i na ovaj način podržavaju.

945
00:41:53,659 --> 00:41:55,739
[SPEAKER_00] A sad se vratimo razgovoru.

946
00:41:55,739 --> 00:41:59,599
[SPEAKER_01] Pa znači ovako, kad se djete rodi,

947
00:41:59,599 --> 00:42:00,920
[SPEAKER_01] ako je sve u redu,

948
00:42:00,920 --> 00:42:03,519
[SPEAKER_01] obično se nakon par dana otpušta kući.

949
00:42:03,519 --> 00:42:06,139
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, obisno da li je normalno se vaginalno rodilo

950
00:42:06,139 --> 00:42:09,519
[SPEAKER_01] ili sekcijom tu varira, ne znam, do tjedan dana,

951
00:42:09,519 --> 00:42:11,599
[SPEAKER_01] ako nije bilo nikakvih komplikacija,

952
00:42:11,599 --> 00:42:14,320
[SPEAKER_01] ako je porodna vrijeme, nije bilo žutila i tako.

953
00:42:14,320 --> 00:42:17,539
[SPEAKER_01] I onda u principu je najbolje prvi pregled

954
00:42:17,539 --> 00:42:19,820
[SPEAKER_01] napraviti u dobi mjesec dana.

955
00:42:19,820 --> 00:42:23,280
[SPEAKER_01] Tada pedijatar procijenjuje sve.

956
00:42:23,280 --> 00:42:25,760
[SPEAKER_01] I koliko je djete dobilo na težini,

957
00:42:25,760 --> 00:42:28,239
[SPEAKER_01] i da li se snalaze dobro u hranjenju,

958
00:42:28,239 --> 00:42:30,519
[SPEAKER_01] i da li je sve neurološki u redu,

959
00:42:30,519 --> 00:42:31,940
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje.

960
00:42:31,940 --> 00:42:34,980
[SPEAKER_01] No, međutim, ako imaju bilo kakve dileme

961
00:42:34,980 --> 00:42:37,300
[SPEAKER_01] roditelji, bilo da dijete, recimo,

962
00:42:37,300 --> 00:42:40,400
[SPEAKER_01] najveći su problemi, da li dovoljno jede,

963
00:42:40,400 --> 00:42:43,380
[SPEAKER_01] ako žele biti, naravno, da mi preporučamo

964
00:42:43,380 --> 00:42:46,440
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek na prsima, ako imaju bilo kakve dileme,

965
00:42:46,440 --> 00:42:48,699
[SPEAKER_01] ne snalaze se s tim ili bebica prva,

966
00:42:48,699 --> 00:42:50,719
[SPEAKER_01] ili ne mora biti prva, drugačija.

967
00:42:50,719 --> 00:42:54,199
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ne ponaša se uopće kao svi koji imaju više djece,

968
00:42:54,199 --> 00:42:57,500
[SPEAKER_01] kažu pa ovo, djetem je potpuno drugačije,

969
00:42:57,500 --> 00:43:00,639
[SPEAKER_01] onda se taj pregled može zakazati i prije.

970
00:43:00,719 --> 00:43:04,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, redovno, nije potrebno prije nego sa mjesec dana.

971
00:43:04,659 --> 00:43:08,260
[SPEAKER_01] Što se tiče patronaže, to u principu,

972
00:43:08,260 --> 00:43:12,579
[SPEAKER_01] patronažna sestra, to se dogovara ovisno gdje se stanuje,

973
00:43:12,579 --> 00:43:16,239
[SPEAKER_01] kad se dijete prijavi, to je u principu prvih tjedan dana

974
00:43:16,239 --> 00:43:17,179
[SPEAKER_01] već ono dolazi.

975
00:43:17,179 --> 00:43:20,300
[SPEAKER_01] Pa sada nekom treba nekoliko dolazaka.

976
00:43:20,300 --> 00:43:23,179
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to se prva dva tjedna sa patronažom,

977
00:43:23,179 --> 00:43:24,099
[SPEAKER_01] ako treba i više.

978
00:43:24,099 --> 00:43:25,840
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kad ona dolazi češće,

979
00:43:25,840 --> 00:43:29,300
[SPEAKER_01] ako nam je dilemica, da li dijete dobro napreduje.

980
00:43:29,300 --> 00:43:32,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ako pupak nije otpao, pa treba možda lapizirati,

981
00:43:32,880 --> 00:43:34,780
[SPEAKER_01] možda čega, ako izgleda inficirano,

982
00:43:34,780 --> 00:43:37,079
[SPEAKER_01] uputiti ranije i liječniku.

983
00:43:37,079 --> 00:43:41,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ako misli da ovo bijelo, što je na jeziku,

984
00:43:41,260 --> 00:43:43,860
[SPEAKER_01] nije samo od hrane, nego da je možda sor.

985
00:43:43,860 --> 00:43:46,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ako oči izgledaju paljene, možda to je samo

986
00:43:46,820 --> 00:43:50,300
[SPEAKER_01] suženje kanalića iz oka, što je vrlo često,

987
00:43:50,300 --> 00:43:53,679
[SPEAKER_01] pa zato oko, ne znam, gnoji ili tako.

988
00:43:53,780 --> 00:43:57,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ali tu će i patronaža biti ta koja je dobra spona,

989
00:43:57,659 --> 00:44:00,559
[SPEAKER_01] da, ako je potrebno, uputi i da kaže,

990
00:44:00,559 --> 00:44:03,159
[SPEAKER_01] mi to imamo isto priliku vidjeti,

991
00:44:03,159 --> 00:44:05,599
[SPEAKER_01] da je zamola i da se oni javljaju ranije,

992
00:44:05,599 --> 00:44:08,960
[SPEAKER_01] ili patronažna sestra rekla da nešto nije u redu.

993
00:44:08,960 --> 00:44:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ili dijete je žuto, pa se sad čini da je jače požutilo,

994
00:44:12,460 --> 00:44:14,440
[SPEAKER_01] nešto da se slabije razbuđuje.

995
00:44:14,960 --> 00:44:17,639
[SPEAKER_01] Znači u toj dobi prvog mjeseca.

996
00:44:17,639 --> 00:44:24,219
[SPEAKER_01] Znači dijete, ono, super je ako jede, spava, plače,

997
00:44:24,219 --> 00:44:28,300
[SPEAKER_01] piški i kaki, sve da nekako normalno dobiva na težini,

998
00:44:28,300 --> 00:44:29,940
[SPEAKER_01] što pogleda patronaža.

999
00:44:29,940 --> 00:44:33,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ako se dijete slabije razbuđuje, ne znam, slabije,

1000
00:44:33,739 --> 00:44:36,260
[SPEAKER_01] mokri, ne možete ga probuditi za obrok,

1001
00:44:36,260 --> 00:44:38,539
[SPEAKER_01] jedva se čini mami, pogotovo oni koji doje,

1002
00:44:38,539 --> 00:44:42,199
[SPEAKER_01] onda nije jadna majka, niti sigur ne li dijete sad spava,

1003
00:44:42,199 --> 00:44:45,099
[SPEAKER_01] malo povuče, koliko je zapravo pojelo.

1004
00:44:45,099 --> 00:44:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] E tu je možda neki alarm da se ipak jave na pregled,

1005
00:44:50,000 --> 00:44:54,159
[SPEAKER_01] da vidimo da je sve ok, jer ovdje može dijete imati i bolest,

1006
00:44:54,159 --> 00:44:57,159
[SPEAKER_01] a da nema povišenu tjelesnu temperaturu.

1007
00:44:57,159 --> 00:45:01,920
[SPEAKER_00] Da, upravo mi je to spominjala u tom kontekstu

1008
00:45:01,920 --> 00:45:07,340
[SPEAKER_00] draga Sonja Buzov, koja je bila u jednoj od prethodnih epizoda.

1009
00:45:08,539 --> 00:45:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] Znam da se i vi poznajete, pratite li i njene skečeve.

1010
00:45:12,159 --> 00:45:13,400
[SPEAKER_00] Je, najbolji su.

1011
00:45:13,400 --> 00:45:15,739
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, pre, pre smiješna je, baš sam joj rekla,

1012
00:45:15,739 --> 00:45:19,320
[SPEAKER_00] on ima posebnu vrstu inteligencije za obraditi takvu temu,

1013
00:45:19,320 --> 00:45:21,500
[SPEAKER_00] savjeta razno raznih.

1014
00:45:21,500 --> 00:45:24,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ona, podsjetilo me sad, ona je rekla da je baš,

1015
00:45:24,079 --> 00:45:28,599
[SPEAKER_00] baš na temelju isključivo majčinske neke intuicije,

1016
00:45:28,599 --> 00:45:32,980
[SPEAKER_00] instinkta se javila, jer joj je bebica bila preuspavana,

1017
00:45:32,980 --> 00:45:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju, evo, super da je se javila.

1018
00:45:37,039 --> 00:45:42,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mislim da uvijek treba slušati roditelje ili mamu,

1019
00:45:42,420 --> 00:45:46,800
[SPEAKER_01] ono kako kažemo, nikad ne, nekako, ma zašto ste došli,

1020
00:45:46,800 --> 00:45:48,960
[SPEAKER_01] niste trebali doći ili šta vas je.

1021
00:45:48,960 --> 00:45:52,699
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što ti vidiš dijete vrlo kratko,

1022
00:45:52,699 --> 00:45:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] čak i kad si njegov pedijatar, vidiš ga tada sat vremena

1023
00:45:56,000 --> 00:45:58,260
[SPEAKER_01] ili ga vidiš na pregledu 15 minuta.

1024
00:45:59,000 --> 00:46:04,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ako netko nešto govori, treba uvijek to pomno poslušati,

1025
00:46:04,579 --> 00:46:08,920
[SPEAKER_01] jer ja se uvijek vodim onom starinskom i stvarno vam nije bez veze,

1026
00:46:08,920 --> 00:46:11,300
[SPEAKER_01] da vam je anamneza pola dijagnoze.

1027
00:46:11,300 --> 00:46:16,280
[SPEAKER_01] Znači naravno da treba znati i pitati roditelja neko pitanje i podpitanje,

1028
00:46:16,380 --> 00:46:20,239
[SPEAKER_01] ali moraju se roditelji poslušati to što kažu,

1029
00:46:20,239 --> 00:46:23,639
[SPEAKER_01] jer oni sigurno nisu došli bez veze, nešto ih je uznemirilo.

1030
00:46:23,639 --> 00:46:26,199
[SPEAKER_01] Pa čak da ispadne na kraju da je sve super,

1031
00:46:26,199 --> 00:46:30,159
[SPEAKER_01] pa to nam je i svima draže, ali treba ih se slušati.

1032
00:46:30,159 --> 00:46:32,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ako je njihova intuicija da nešto nije u redu,

1033
00:46:32,559 --> 00:46:38,400
[SPEAKER_01] pogledat sve, pomno poslušat, a onda reći sve u redu, ako je.

1034
00:46:38,760 --> 00:46:47,039
[SPEAKER_00] Je vam se dogodilo to da je roditelj na kraju bio u pravu

1035
00:46:47,039 --> 00:46:49,440
[SPEAKER_00] nakon što je došao, ne znam, kod vas na drugo, treće,

1036
00:46:49,440 --> 00:46:52,320
[SPEAKER_00] koje je mišljenje, a da su prije toga ih odbili

1037
00:46:52,320 --> 00:46:56,820
[SPEAKER_00] i na kraju da je ipak presudila ta intuicija?

1038
00:46:56,820 --> 00:47:00,079
[SPEAKER_01] Je, desi se, desi se, ali desi se i ono brnuto,

1039
00:47:00,079 --> 00:47:02,880
[SPEAKER_01] samo ja uvijek se slušam, desi se i da su došli, ne znam,

1040
00:47:02,880 --> 00:47:06,880
[SPEAKER_01] jel su se uplašili, zato nekad internet može biti dobar,

1041
00:47:07,480 --> 00:47:10,159
[SPEAKER_01] ali i loš, uplašili su se da djete, ne znam,

1042
00:47:10,159 --> 00:47:15,300
[SPEAKER_01] ubrzano dišeli, loše snimali, znači vidli pa su otišli u bolnicu,

1043
00:47:15,300 --> 00:47:19,239
[SPEAKER_01] čekali, a sve normalno, znači postoje te faze

1044
00:47:19,239 --> 00:47:22,079
[SPEAKER_01] periodičkog ubrzanog disanja kod malog novorođenčeta

1045
00:47:22,079 --> 00:47:26,940
[SPEAKER_01] koje nije patologija, znači, ili zvukovi koje beba proizvodi,

1046
00:47:26,940 --> 00:47:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] toga se znaju uplašiti.

1047
00:47:29,000 --> 00:47:32,119
[SPEAKER_01] Vi ste iskusna mama, pa znate da u prvom mjesecu,

1048
00:47:32,119 --> 00:47:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] čak i kasnije od tog nekog roktanja, hroptanja, nalik na različite životinje,

1049
00:47:37,480 --> 00:47:41,420
[SPEAKER_01] imamo zvukove, a da nije nešto ozbiljno.

1050
00:47:41,420 --> 00:47:43,679
[SPEAKER_01] Djeta se samo praži.

1051
00:47:43,679 --> 00:47:49,380
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, ali onda ih podučiš, kako prepoznamo da nije ništa i zašto,

1052
00:47:49,380 --> 00:47:52,159
[SPEAKER_01] kako premijenimo poziciju kad je nešto ozbiljno,

1053
00:47:52,619 --> 00:47:58,360
[SPEAKER_01] ili taj nos zbog mekanih hrskavica, recimo, onako hropta i sad oni stave ruku na prsa.

1054
00:47:58,360 --> 00:48:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je sve malo i tu se vibracije prenose i tebi se čini stvarno da hropti u prsima.

1055
00:48:05,000 --> 00:48:06,139
[SPEAKER_01] A nije.

1056
00:48:06,139 --> 00:48:09,559
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, lako je to reći kad se posluša, ali onda ih se poduči.

1057
00:48:09,559 --> 00:48:11,300
[SPEAKER_01] Kako kad premijenimo poziciju,

1058
00:48:11,300 --> 00:48:14,179
[SPEAKER_01] kako sve nestane, ako bebica može normalno jesti,

1059
00:48:14,179 --> 00:48:16,219
[SPEAKER_01] onda nije sigurno bolestan nos,

1060
00:48:16,219 --> 00:48:18,679
[SPEAKER_01] ili beba ne bi mogla sisati da imamo...

1061
00:48:18,679 --> 00:48:22,039
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, beba uopće ne može jesti ako ona hroptina nosi,

1062
00:48:22,039 --> 00:48:25,340
[SPEAKER_01] nos je pun ili je sluznica jako upaljena i nos je zaštopan.

1063
00:48:25,340 --> 00:48:29,699
[SPEAKER_00] Meni su ti zvukići čak bili simpatični,

1064
00:48:29,699 --> 00:48:32,239
[SPEAKER_00] ali ovo ubrzano disanje ne toliko.

1065
00:48:32,239 --> 00:48:37,239
[SPEAKER_00] Baš mi je bilo strah bronhiolitisa ili RS virusa?

1066
00:48:37,539 --> 00:48:38,639
[SPEAKER_00] To nije ista stvar, je li tako?

1067
00:48:38,639 --> 00:48:41,260
[SPEAKER_01] Je, nije ista stvar.

1068
00:48:41,260 --> 00:48:46,159
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, bronhiolitis je upala najmanjih dišnjih puteva,

1069
00:48:46,159 --> 00:48:49,420
[SPEAKER_01] bronhiola, to su oni skroz blizu alveolama,

1070
00:48:49,420 --> 00:48:50,639
[SPEAKER_01] to jest plučima.

1071
00:48:50,639 --> 00:48:55,019
[SPEAKER_01] I najčešći uzročnik takve pojave bronhiolitisa

1072
00:48:55,019 --> 00:48:57,320
[SPEAKER_01] je respiratorni sicicijski virus,

1073
00:48:57,320 --> 00:48:59,340
[SPEAKER_01] to jest RSV, kratica.

1074
00:48:59,340 --> 00:49:01,139
[SPEAKER_01] Zato ste ovoga misli.

1075
00:49:01,139 --> 00:49:03,900
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, to ga mi je bilo užasno strah na početku.

1076
00:49:03,900 --> 00:49:06,940
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, respiratorni sicicijski virus,

1077
00:49:07,199 --> 00:49:08,820
[SPEAKER_01] da dobijemo nas dvije,

1078
00:49:08,820 --> 00:49:11,199
[SPEAKER_01] mi možda imamo samo prehladu i suri nam nos.

1079
00:49:11,199 --> 00:49:15,239
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, neko vrtičko dijete možda usurenje nosa

1080
00:49:15,239 --> 00:49:17,559
[SPEAKER_01] može kašljati ili imati, ne znam,

1081
00:49:17,559 --> 00:49:20,900
[SPEAKER_01] zvukove to kašlja kao da su napadnute glasnice

1082
00:49:20,900 --> 00:49:22,119
[SPEAKER_01] pa da je laringitis.

1083
00:49:22,119 --> 00:49:26,079
[SPEAKER_01] A manja djeca, osobito dojenčat,

1084
00:49:26,079 --> 00:49:29,619
[SPEAKER_01] znači, iako su ranije rođena, tim više,

1085
00:49:29,619 --> 00:49:33,219
[SPEAKER_01] njima se taj infekt, koja je glavna opasnost,

1086
00:49:33,219 --> 00:49:35,460
[SPEAKER_01] zašto onda nekad vrtičko dijete,

1087
00:49:35,539 --> 00:49:38,699
[SPEAKER_01] zašto kažemo te skroz male da ne idu dok su prehlađeni,

1088
00:49:38,699 --> 00:49:41,260
[SPEAKER_01] recimo, njima samo curi nos od RSV-a,

1089
00:49:41,260 --> 00:49:44,119
[SPEAKER_01] a mala bebica koja ima dva mjeseca,

1090
00:49:44,119 --> 00:49:48,300
[SPEAKER_01] ako dobije takav virus, znači, putevi znamo da su

1091
00:49:48,300 --> 00:49:52,800
[SPEAKER_01] puno manji, puno uži i taj virus se puno lakše spusti

1092
00:49:52,800 --> 00:49:54,699
[SPEAKER_01] na donje dišne puteve.

1093
00:49:54,699 --> 00:49:58,099
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, kad vi imate puteve dišne koji su jako uski

1094
00:49:58,099 --> 00:50:02,380
[SPEAKER_01] i sad napadne ih virus, taj virus napravi upalu sluznice

1095
00:50:02,380 --> 00:50:04,460
[SPEAKER_01] koja onda otekne, to se zove DM,

1096
00:50:04,659 --> 00:50:06,480
[SPEAKER_01] i dolazi do produkcije sluzi.

1097
00:50:06,480 --> 00:50:09,420
[SPEAKER_01] Na taj način se ti putevi zaštopavaju,

1098
00:50:09,420 --> 00:50:15,960
[SPEAKER_01] ne može se normalno obskrbiti sa kisikom alveolice

1099
00:50:15,960 --> 00:50:18,820
[SPEAKER_01] i dijete da bi to moglo postići,

1100
00:50:18,820 --> 00:50:21,380
[SPEAKER_01] znači počinje onda ubrzano disati,

1101
00:50:21,380 --> 00:50:24,039
[SPEAKER_01] plitko i brzo, sve brže, brže, brže,

1102
00:50:24,039 --> 00:50:26,420
[SPEAKER_01] znači koristi ono što mi kažemo,

1103
00:50:26,420 --> 00:50:28,599
[SPEAKER_01] pomoćnu respiratornu muskulaturu,

1104
00:50:28,599 --> 00:50:31,219
[SPEAKER_01] pa mi možemo vidjeti dijete koja je mala bebica

1105
00:50:31,219 --> 00:50:32,940
[SPEAKER_01] da je bolesna od bronhiolitisa,

1106
00:50:32,940 --> 00:50:36,559
[SPEAKER_01] da diše brzo, plitko, da stenje,

1107
00:50:36,559 --> 00:50:38,920
[SPEAKER_01] jer se tako omogućava, znači tiskanjem

1108
00:50:38,920 --> 00:50:43,119
[SPEAKER_01] da možda još uspije obskrbiti organizam kisikom,

1109
00:50:43,119 --> 00:50:46,579
[SPEAKER_01] koristi svu pomoćnu respiratornu muskulaturu,

1110
00:50:46,579 --> 00:50:49,460
[SPEAKER_01] pa ono što mi možemo vidjeti da klima glavicom,

1111
00:50:49,460 --> 00:50:52,840
[SPEAKER_01] da se šire nosnice, da diše trbuhom,

1112
00:50:52,840 --> 00:50:55,980
[SPEAKER_01] da se uvlače međurebreni mišići,

1113
00:50:56,320 --> 00:50:58,400
[SPEAKER_01] jugulum često ne možemo vidjeti,

1114
00:50:58,400 --> 00:51:00,219
[SPEAKER_01] jer bebica ono nema vrat,

1115
00:51:00,219 --> 00:51:02,820
[SPEAKER_01] onako je sve spojeno i ovoga,

1116
00:51:02,820 --> 00:51:05,679
[SPEAKER_01] tako i nekad ima pjenicu na ustima

1117
00:51:05,679 --> 00:51:08,440
[SPEAKER_01] i zapravo je više bebica klonula

1118
00:51:08,440 --> 00:51:09,519
[SPEAKER_01] i ne može jesti,

1119
00:51:09,519 --> 00:51:11,699
[SPEAKER_01] znači ona je toliko angažirana sa disanjem

1120
00:51:11,699 --> 00:51:12,860
[SPEAKER_01] da ne može jesti,

1121
00:51:12,860 --> 00:51:16,900
[SPEAKER_01] mislim to je stanje da je to odmah za bolnicu.

1122
00:51:16,900 --> 00:51:21,179
[SPEAKER_01] Ako neko dobije blagi respiratorni infekt,

1123
00:51:21,179 --> 00:51:23,480
[SPEAKER_01] znamo da braco ima nos,

1124
00:51:23,480 --> 00:51:25,699
[SPEAKER_01] da recimo je to RSV,

1125
00:51:25,800 --> 00:51:27,880
[SPEAKER_01] danas postoje razni te brzi testovi,

1126
00:51:27,880 --> 00:51:30,900
[SPEAKER_01] ne mora značiti da nužno će mala beba

1127
00:51:30,900 --> 00:51:33,139
[SPEAKER_01] dobiti stanje da je to za bolnicu.

1128
00:51:33,139 --> 00:51:35,119
[SPEAKER_01] Možda će joj malo curit nos,

1129
00:51:35,119 --> 00:51:37,940
[SPEAKER_01] imaće blago koji zvižduk ili malo sekreta,

1130
00:51:37,940 --> 00:51:40,940
[SPEAKER_01] koji će roditelj sam sa inhalacijom,

1131
00:51:40,940 --> 00:51:45,400
[SPEAKER_01] izotonim ili hiperotonim otopinama mora,

1132
00:51:45,400 --> 00:51:47,400
[SPEAKER_01] moć na vlaži dišne puteve,

1133
00:51:47,400 --> 00:51:48,840
[SPEAKER_01] smanjiti otok sluznice,

1134
00:51:48,840 --> 00:51:51,400
[SPEAKER_01] iščistiti sekret, bebica ćemo čijesti,

1135
00:51:51,400 --> 00:51:54,780
[SPEAKER_01] jer to je zapravo samo izliječiva bolest koja prođe.

1136
00:51:54,780 --> 00:51:59,159
[SPEAKER_01] Samo je pitanje koliko teška je u toj maloj dobi.

1137
00:51:59,940 --> 00:52:05,300
[SPEAKER_00] Jesu li okej one šprice koje, ono kao potisak se napravi,

1138
00:52:05,300 --> 00:52:09,099
[SPEAKER_00] kroz jednu nosnicu se ubaci, ne znam ova, fiziološka,

1139
00:52:09,099 --> 00:52:12,340
[SPEAKER_00] pada na drugu stranu iziđe sekret.

1140
00:52:12,820 --> 00:52:17,019
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ja sam to tek možda nedavno vidjela,

1141
00:52:17,019 --> 00:52:18,840
[SPEAKER_00] da je se populariziralo,

1142
00:52:18,840 --> 00:52:22,800
[SPEAKER_00] ali nisam sigur,

1143
00:52:22,800 --> 00:52:24,360
[SPEAKER_00] mislim, evo, ne znam, vi recite,

1144
00:52:24,360 --> 00:52:26,719
[SPEAKER_00] jer nekad mi se djete tu krene kao,

1145
00:52:26,719 --> 00:52:27,739
[SPEAKER_00] joj mama vrti mi se,

1146
00:52:27,739 --> 00:52:29,920
[SPEAKER_00] onda sad u zadnjem vrijeme ne radim to,

1147
00:52:29,920 --> 00:52:30,860
[SPEAKER_00] jer mi ga je malo žao,

1148
00:52:30,860 --> 00:52:33,300
[SPEAKER_00] iako vidim te silne na internetu videe,

1149
00:52:33,300 --> 00:52:35,880
[SPEAKER_00] gdje djete ono sa smiješkom izbaci hrpetinu toga,

1150
00:52:35,880 --> 00:52:37,280
[SPEAKER_00] i mislim si, ja bi to naređe,

1151
00:52:37,280 --> 00:52:40,579
[SPEAKER_00] ono, ta satisfakcija kad djete izbaci te guste sline van,

1152
00:52:41,780 --> 00:52:43,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kad mi je rekao ono, vrti mi se,

1153
00:52:43,760 --> 00:52:45,519
[SPEAKER_00] onda ne znam kako je to.

1154
00:52:45,519 --> 00:52:46,880
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, to je dosta individualno,

1155
00:52:46,880 --> 00:52:50,539
[SPEAKER_01] možda ako djeca to prihvaćaju,

1156
00:52:50,539 --> 00:52:53,159
[SPEAKER_01] i da se može, možeš jako dobro oprati nos,

1157
00:52:53,159 --> 00:52:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] no, međutim, vi tu idete i prema uhuma,

1158
00:52:56,000 --> 00:52:56,940
[SPEAKER_01] znači može ući,

1159
00:52:56,940 --> 00:52:58,500
[SPEAKER_01] ali tu je ustahjeva tubica,

1160
00:52:58,500 --> 00:53:01,320
[SPEAKER_01] koja povezuje nos sa srednjim uhom,

1161
00:53:01,320 --> 00:53:02,559
[SPEAKER_01] pa vi može ući tako,

1162
00:53:02,559 --> 00:53:06,139
[SPEAKER_01] mi možemo i napraviti to da nam ne dijele baš,

1163
00:53:06,139 --> 00:53:07,340
[SPEAKER_01] zato je on rekao, vrti mi se,

1164
00:53:07,340 --> 00:53:08,619
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne mogu reći da je ugodo,

1165
00:53:08,619 --> 00:53:09,780
[SPEAKER_01] i neka djeca vrišta,

1166
00:53:09,880 --> 00:53:12,199
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam osobno više pobornik

1167
00:53:12,199 --> 00:53:15,780
[SPEAKER_01] da se koriste izotone otopine koje vlaže,

1168
00:53:15,780 --> 00:53:18,519
[SPEAKER_01] ili hipertone u obliku sprejeva,

1169
00:53:18,519 --> 00:53:20,800
[SPEAKER_01] i na taj način se smanju otok sluznice,

1170
00:53:20,800 --> 00:53:25,139
[SPEAKER_01] i da se sekret izvadi sa aspiratorom.

1171
00:53:25,340 --> 00:53:26,980
[SPEAKER_01] prije, ako ne može djete,

1172
00:53:26,980 --> 00:53:29,840
[SPEAKER_01] ako još ne zna koje maleno puhati nos,

1173
00:53:29,840 --> 00:53:33,500
[SPEAKER_01] nego baš te velike šprise nije ugodno.

1174
00:53:33,500 --> 00:53:35,559
[SPEAKER_00] Drago mi je da ste spomenuli malo prije ovo,

1175
00:53:35,559 --> 00:53:39,300
[SPEAKER_00] kako na odraslu osobu to ne mora nikako ućecat,

1176
00:53:39,300 --> 00:53:40,900
[SPEAKER_00] može zakašljeti dva, tri puta,

1177
00:53:40,900 --> 00:53:43,880
[SPEAKER_00] a bebici može biti stvarno problem.

1178
00:53:45,179 --> 00:53:47,500
[SPEAKER_00] što nas dovodi do pitanja posjeta

1179
00:53:47,500 --> 00:53:51,920
[SPEAKER_00] odraslih ljudi, prijatelja, rodbine sa djecom,

1180
00:53:51,920 --> 00:53:52,460
[SPEAKER_00] što više,

1181
00:53:52,460 --> 00:53:56,019
[SPEAKER_00] kod ljudi koji su tek dobili malu bebicu.

1182
00:53:56,820 --> 00:53:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ili evo da se prebacimo u perspektivu nekoga

1183
00:53:59,099 --> 00:54:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] koji je dobio novorođenče,

1184
00:54:01,039 --> 00:54:01,699
[SPEAKER_00] pri novu.

1185
00:54:01,699 --> 00:54:05,039
[SPEAKER_00] Kada zvati prijatelje u koste?

1186
00:54:05,039 --> 00:54:09,639
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, prije nego što odgovorite,

1187
00:54:09,639 --> 00:54:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] ja ću reći svoje iskustvo.

1188
00:54:11,380 --> 00:54:13,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam zagovarala kao ne, ne,

1189
00:54:13,559 --> 00:54:16,159
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo jer ovaj mlađi je rođen doslovno na Božić,

1190
00:54:16,159 --> 00:54:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] zima je, svi su polubolesni.

1191
00:54:18,619 --> 00:54:20,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ali onda kad sam došla doma,

1192
00:54:20,579 --> 00:54:22,099
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam se poželjela ljudi

1193
00:54:22,099 --> 00:54:24,260
[SPEAKER_00] i dobro sam se osjećala

1194
00:54:24,260 --> 00:54:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] i htjela sam da dođu.

1195
00:54:25,420 --> 00:54:27,760
[SPEAKER_00] I došli su i okej, nije on tad zaradio taj virus,

1196
00:54:27,760 --> 00:54:28,840
[SPEAKER_00] nego nekad malo kasnije.

1197
00:54:28,840 --> 00:54:31,780
[SPEAKER_00] I onda sam počela savjetovat,

1198
00:54:31,780 --> 00:54:34,400
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno dijelit svoje mišljenje drugima

1199
00:54:34,400 --> 00:54:36,099
[SPEAKER_00] da kako god se ti osjećaš.

1200
00:54:36,099 --> 00:54:38,960
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, je li to pametan savjet uopće

1201
00:54:38,960 --> 00:54:42,460
[SPEAKER_00] ili treba pričekat sa posjetama?

1202
00:54:42,460 --> 00:54:44,219
[SPEAKER_01] Pa recimo,

1203
00:54:44,219 --> 00:54:45,699
[SPEAKER_01] osobno mislim da posjeti

1204
00:54:45,699 --> 00:54:48,559
[SPEAKER_01] koji nije najužar odbina prije

1205
00:54:48,559 --> 00:54:50,460
[SPEAKER_01] nego što dijete na vrši mjesec dana

1206
00:54:50,460 --> 00:54:52,599
[SPEAKER_01] nisu potrebne i poželjne,

1207
00:54:52,599 --> 00:54:54,760
[SPEAKER_01] a i kasnije kad vam dolaze gosti,

1208
00:54:54,820 --> 00:54:56,039
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da je u redu

1209
00:54:56,039 --> 00:54:58,119
[SPEAKER_01] da čovjek sam bude

1210
00:54:58,119 --> 00:55:00,239
[SPEAKER_01] toliko samosvjestan

1211
00:55:00,239 --> 00:55:02,199
[SPEAKER_01] da ako je prehlađen

1212
00:55:02,199 --> 00:55:03,380
[SPEAKER_01] i osjeća se loše

1213
00:55:03,380 --> 00:55:05,159
[SPEAKER_01] ili su mu djeca prehlađena,

1214
00:55:05,159 --> 00:55:06,739
[SPEAKER_01] da odgodi tu posjetu.

1215
00:55:06,739 --> 00:55:08,579
[SPEAKER_01] Jednostavno,

1216
00:55:08,579 --> 00:55:11,159
[SPEAKER_01] same takve virusne infekcije

1217
00:55:11,159 --> 00:55:13,300
[SPEAKER_01] koje najčešće prenosioci su

1218
00:55:13,300 --> 00:55:14,300
[SPEAKER_01] više mala djeca,

1219
00:55:14,300 --> 00:55:15,260
[SPEAKER_01] osobito vrtička,

1220
00:55:15,260 --> 00:55:17,079
[SPEAKER_01] one se prenose zrakom.

1221
00:55:17,280 --> 00:55:19,099
[SPEAKER_01] Znači tu ne mora biti direktan kontakt,

1222
00:55:19,099 --> 00:55:20,860
[SPEAKER_01] pa ako to dijete šmrca,

1223
00:55:20,860 --> 00:55:21,980
[SPEAKER_01] kiše i kašlje,

1224
00:55:21,980 --> 00:55:23,739
[SPEAKER_01] vama će prostorija biti

1225
00:55:23,739 --> 00:55:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] od čestica.

1226
00:55:25,000 --> 00:55:27,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, može biti da nije u istoj prostoriji

1227
00:55:27,199 --> 00:55:28,039
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je bebica,

1228
00:55:28,039 --> 00:55:29,619
[SPEAKER_01] pa ćete vi to proluftati,

1229
00:55:29,619 --> 00:55:31,480
[SPEAKER_01] počistiti i onda više

1230
00:55:31,480 --> 00:55:32,659
[SPEAKER_01] nije soba.

1231
00:55:32,860 --> 00:55:35,619
[SPEAKER_01] ali nekako najbliži

1232
00:55:35,619 --> 00:55:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] u ovoga rođaci bida dolaze,

1233
00:55:39,000 --> 00:55:40,360
[SPEAKER_01] ali ono nešto velike,

1234
00:55:40,360 --> 00:55:42,159
[SPEAKER_01] neke posjete s malom bebom.

1235
00:55:42,159 --> 00:55:44,300
[SPEAKER_00] Radi je ne.

1236
00:55:44,300 --> 00:55:45,280
[SPEAKER_01] Radi je ne.

1237
00:55:45,280 --> 00:55:47,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ako su bolesni.

1238
00:55:47,039 --> 00:55:48,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ili s maskom.

1239
00:55:48,840 --> 00:55:50,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ili maska ne vrijedi.

1240
00:55:50,019 --> 00:55:51,800
[SPEAKER_01] A maske ovisi.

1241
00:55:51,800 --> 00:55:53,340
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, malo mi je to isto onako

1242
00:55:53,340 --> 00:55:54,659
[SPEAKER_01] da vam dođe neko u goste

1243
00:55:54,659 --> 00:55:55,440
[SPEAKER_01] baš s maskom.

1244
00:55:55,440 --> 00:55:57,039
[SPEAKER_01] Znači jednostavno, ok,

1245
00:55:57,039 --> 00:55:57,980
[SPEAKER_01] pogledaju bebu,

1246
00:55:57,980 --> 00:56:00,300
[SPEAKER_01] ali možda ne moraju bebu nošat,

1247
00:56:00,300 --> 00:56:02,199
[SPEAKER_01] ljubit, ljubit joj rukice.

1248
00:56:02,199 --> 00:56:03,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ako beba ima dva mjeseca,

1249
00:56:03,539 --> 00:56:05,840
[SPEAKER_01] znate da ono počinje onaj period

1250
00:56:05,840 --> 00:56:07,480
[SPEAKER_01] kad stavlja rukice u usta.

1251
00:56:07,480 --> 00:56:09,239
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, u tom smislu.

1252
00:56:09,239 --> 00:56:09,800
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

1253
00:56:09,800 --> 00:56:11,679
[SPEAKER_00] Odmah apel svima,

1254
00:56:11,679 --> 00:56:13,019
[SPEAKER_00] ne ljubite male bebe

1255
00:56:13,019 --> 00:56:14,400
[SPEAKER_00] kad dođete u goste.

1256
00:56:14,400 --> 00:56:15,639
[SPEAKER_00] Nema potrebe.

1257
00:56:15,639 --> 00:56:17,380
[SPEAKER_00] Malo pomazite preko robice

1258
00:56:17,380 --> 00:56:19,340
[SPEAKER_00] i beba će biti sretna.

1259
00:56:19,340 --> 00:56:20,900
[SPEAKER_00] U glavu, onak sa strane.

1260
00:56:20,900 --> 00:56:21,780
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

1261
00:56:21,780 --> 00:56:24,460
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ste majka trojčeka.

1262
00:56:24,460 --> 00:56:25,659
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

1263
00:56:25,659 --> 00:56:27,199
[SPEAKER_00] Recite mi jeste li se vi držali

1264
00:56:27,199 --> 00:56:28,880
[SPEAKER_00] ovog vlastitog savjeta

1265
00:56:28,880 --> 00:56:30,940
[SPEAKER_00] koliko je prošlo od

1266
00:56:30,940 --> 00:56:33,460
[SPEAKER_00] dolazka bebica,

1267
00:56:33,460 --> 00:56:34,719
[SPEAKER_00] ipak puta tri.

1268
00:56:34,719 --> 00:56:36,760
[SPEAKER_00] Je li bilo tri mjeseca čekanja?

1269
00:56:36,760 --> 00:56:38,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ubiti, uvedite jednost malo.

1270
00:56:38,820 --> 00:56:40,039
[SPEAKER_00] Kakva je priča?

1271
00:56:40,039 --> 00:56:42,260
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto sam,

1272
00:56:42,260 --> 00:56:44,280
[SPEAKER_00] ako sam dobro zapamtila,

1273
00:56:44,280 --> 00:56:46,219
[SPEAKER_00] u razgovoru ste spomenuli

1274
00:56:46,219 --> 00:56:48,280
[SPEAKER_00] prije snimanja da su i ranje rođeni,

1275
00:56:48,280 --> 00:56:48,800
[SPEAKER_00] je li tako?

1276
00:56:48,800 --> 00:56:50,679
[SPEAKER_00] Onda to pretpostavlja malo rugačije

1277
00:56:50,679 --> 00:56:51,719
[SPEAKER_00] sve skupa izgleda, je li da?

1278
00:56:51,719 --> 00:56:52,219
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

1279
00:56:52,219 --> 00:56:54,380
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ja sam mama trojčeka,

1280
00:56:54,380 --> 00:56:57,900
[SPEAKER_01] koji su sada 22 godine prošli

1281
00:56:57,900 --> 00:56:58,900
[SPEAKER_01] i studenti svi.

1282
00:56:58,900 --> 00:57:01,760
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to kada je bilo,

1283
00:57:01,760 --> 00:57:03,360
[SPEAKER_01] evo samo malo da se prisjetim,

1284
00:57:03,360 --> 00:57:04,900
[SPEAKER_01] jer to vam tako brzo prođe.

1285
00:57:04,900 --> 00:57:05,980
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, naravno,

1286
00:57:05,980 --> 00:57:07,139
[SPEAKER_01] ranije su se rodili,

1287
00:57:07,139 --> 00:57:08,800
[SPEAKER_01] u 33. tjednu,

1288
00:57:08,800 --> 00:57:10,239
[SPEAKER_01] jer jednostavno je nemoguće,

1289
00:57:10,239 --> 00:57:12,480
[SPEAKER_01] kad su više plodne trudnoće,

1290
00:57:12,480 --> 00:57:14,719
[SPEAKER_01] gotovo iznijesti do kraja.

1291
00:57:14,719 --> 00:57:15,980
[SPEAKER_01] Kad su se rodili,

1292
00:57:15,980 --> 00:57:18,820
[SPEAKER_01] oni su težili svi oko kilu i pol.

1293
00:57:18,820 --> 00:57:20,639
[SPEAKER_01] Bili su vrlo male razlike.

1294
00:57:20,639 --> 00:57:22,880
[SPEAKER_01] Zbog svoje nezrelosti

1295
00:57:22,880 --> 00:57:24,860
[SPEAKER_01] još nisu znali niti sisati.

1296
00:57:24,860 --> 00:57:27,440
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, bili su smješteni inkubatori,

1297
00:57:27,440 --> 00:57:29,079
[SPEAKER_01] hranjeni na sondu.

1298
00:57:29,079 --> 00:57:32,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ali su vrlo brzo sve svladali

1299
00:57:32,039 --> 00:57:33,900
[SPEAKER_01] i kad su došli do nekih

1300
00:57:33,900 --> 00:57:35,739
[SPEAKER_01] dvije kile i dvijesto, tristo,

1301
00:57:35,739 --> 00:57:38,599
[SPEAKER_01] su zapravo bili spremni za doma.

1302
00:57:38,599 --> 00:57:39,500
[SPEAKER_01] A što ste rekli,

1303
00:57:39,500 --> 00:57:41,139
[SPEAKER_01] koliko dugo su bili u inkubatoru?

1304
00:57:41,139 --> 00:57:42,500
[SPEAKER_01] To je trebalo oko mjesec dana.

1305
00:57:42,500 --> 00:57:44,280
[SPEAKER_01] Oko mjesec dana da su oni

1306
00:57:44,280 --> 00:57:45,420
[SPEAKER_01] u početku jeli.

1307
00:57:45,420 --> 00:57:47,320
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to vam se daje na sondicu

1308
00:57:47,320 --> 00:57:50,400
[SPEAKER_01] po pet mililitra mlijekeca.

1309
00:57:50,400 --> 00:57:53,159
[SPEAKER_01] I ovoga, kad su došli kući,

1310
00:57:53,159 --> 00:57:55,800
[SPEAKER_01] ja, nažalost, nisam mogla baš sve

1311
00:57:55,800 --> 00:57:57,059
[SPEAKER_01] da niko ne dolazi.

1312
00:57:57,059 --> 00:57:59,360
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što kad imaš samo dvoja,

1313
00:57:59,360 --> 00:58:00,420
[SPEAKER_01] to je tata i mama,

1314
00:58:00,420 --> 00:58:02,360
[SPEAKER_01] i tri bebice od dvije

1315
00:58:02,360 --> 00:58:04,659
[SPEAKER_01] i niti dvije i po kile,

1316
00:58:04,659 --> 00:58:07,460
[SPEAKER_01] ti zapravo fale ti uvijek jedne ruke.

1317
00:58:07,460 --> 00:58:09,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, dvije ruke ti fale.

1318
00:58:09,639 --> 00:58:12,059
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ti ne možeš ovoga

1319
00:58:12,059 --> 00:58:13,460
[SPEAKER_01] kada jednog hraniš,

1320
00:58:13,840 --> 00:58:16,380
[SPEAKER_01] znači i drugi hrani drugoga.

1321
00:58:16,380 --> 00:58:18,280
[SPEAKER_01] Ako treći počne plakati,

1322
00:58:18,280 --> 00:58:19,659
[SPEAKER_01] a znaš da je gladan,

1323
00:58:19,659 --> 00:58:20,460
[SPEAKER_01] to je strašno.

1324
00:58:20,460 --> 00:58:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je jedino z čega se sjećam.

1325
00:58:22,000 --> 00:58:22,900
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da je tu

1326
00:58:22,900 --> 00:58:24,900
[SPEAKER_01] u našim početcima

1327
00:58:24,900 --> 00:58:26,219
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek bio neko.

1328
00:58:26,219 --> 00:58:26,860
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su, znači,

1329
00:58:26,860 --> 00:58:28,679
[SPEAKER_01] bili mjesec dana otprilike.

1330
00:58:28,679 --> 00:58:30,260
[SPEAKER_01] Kad su došli kući,

1331
00:58:30,260 --> 00:58:31,860
[SPEAKER_01] tu je bila ili moja mama,

1332
00:58:31,860 --> 00:58:33,300
[SPEAKER_01] ili sestra,

1333
00:58:33,300 --> 00:58:35,340
[SPEAKER_01] onda ubrzo dadilja,

1334
00:58:35,340 --> 00:58:37,460
[SPEAKER_01] koju smo imali dugo,

1335
00:58:37,460 --> 00:58:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] bila do 12. godine.

1336
00:58:39,079 --> 00:58:41,920
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo je bila naša dadilja baka,

1337
00:58:41,920 --> 00:58:42,760
[SPEAKER_01] sve njima.

1338
00:58:43,619 --> 00:58:44,579
[SPEAKER_01] ali ovoga,

1339
00:58:44,579 --> 00:58:45,400
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1340
00:58:45,400 --> 00:58:46,480
[SPEAKER_01] to je u početku

1341
00:58:46,480 --> 00:58:47,960
[SPEAKER_01] bio izazov sve.

1342
00:58:47,960 --> 00:58:48,579
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1343
00:58:48,579 --> 00:58:49,519
[SPEAKER_01] li smo oni jeli

1344
00:58:49,519 --> 00:58:51,199
[SPEAKER_01] 40 mililitra

1345
00:58:51,199 --> 00:58:52,960
[SPEAKER_01] po 40 minuta.

1346
00:58:52,960 --> 00:58:53,380
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1347
00:58:53,380 --> 00:58:55,159
[SPEAKER_01] kao ti gledaš u tu bočicu,

1348
00:58:55,159 --> 00:58:56,039
[SPEAKER_01] kao da stoji.

1349
00:58:56,559 --> 00:58:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali onda,

1350
00:58:57,000 --> 00:58:58,780
[SPEAKER_01] to brzo sve prođe.

1351
00:58:58,780 --> 00:58:59,800
[SPEAKER_01] Već za mjesec,

1352
00:58:59,800 --> 00:59:00,039
[SPEAKER_01] dva,

1353
00:59:00,039 --> 00:59:01,699
[SPEAKER_01] to je puno brže.

1354
00:59:01,699 --> 00:59:02,940
[SPEAKER_01] Samo nekada to

1355
00:59:02,940 --> 00:59:04,280
[SPEAKER_01] ili presvlačiš,

1356
00:59:04,280 --> 00:59:05,219
[SPEAKER_01] ili hraniš.

1357
00:59:05,219 --> 00:59:05,579
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1358
00:59:05,579 --> 00:59:06,840
[SPEAKER_01] nema razlike dan,

1359
00:59:06,840 --> 00:59:07,360
[SPEAKER_01] noć.

1360
00:59:07,360 --> 00:59:09,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ali sve se to nekako.

1361
00:59:09,079 --> 00:59:10,599
[SPEAKER_01] Imali su jake grčeve,

1362
00:59:10,599 --> 00:59:11,820
[SPEAKER_01] ili su bili mali,

1363
00:59:11,820 --> 00:59:13,340
[SPEAKER_01] crjeva su bila nezrela.

1364
00:59:13,340 --> 00:59:14,840
[SPEAKER_01] Tad je postojao

1365
00:59:14,840 --> 00:59:16,599
[SPEAKER_01] samo jedan preparat.

1366
00:59:16,599 --> 00:59:17,219
[SPEAKER_01] To je bio

1367
00:59:17,219 --> 00:59:18,260
[SPEAKER_01] Subsimpleks,

1368
00:59:18,260 --> 00:59:18,940
[SPEAKER_01] koji je još uvijek

1369
00:59:18,940 --> 00:59:19,679
[SPEAKER_01] na tržištu.

1370
00:59:19,679 --> 00:59:20,500
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno,

1371
00:59:20,500 --> 00:59:22,159
[SPEAKER_01] da smo to davali,

1372
00:59:22,159 --> 00:59:23,199
[SPEAKER_01] jer jednostavno,

1373
00:59:23,199 --> 00:59:24,760
[SPEAKER_01] jako je teško gledati

1374
00:59:24,760 --> 00:59:26,119
[SPEAKER_01] kad je beba mala

1375
00:59:26,119 --> 00:59:27,639
[SPEAKER_01] i toliko jako plače.

1376
00:59:27,639 --> 00:59:29,119
[SPEAKER_00] A ovih mjesec dana,

1377
00:59:29,119 --> 00:59:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] vi ste bili doma,

1378
00:59:30,559 --> 00:59:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] pa dolazili ili kako?

1379
00:59:32,000 --> 00:59:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam dolazila,

1380
00:59:33,000 --> 00:59:33,440
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1381
00:59:33,440 --> 00:59:34,820
[SPEAKER_01] da se učim hraniti.

1382
00:59:34,820 --> 00:59:36,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam čak i dojila.

1383
00:59:36,840 --> 00:59:38,880
[SPEAKER_01] Prva četiri mjeseca,

1384
00:59:38,880 --> 00:59:40,880
[SPEAKER_01] onda je to jednostavno

1385
00:59:40,880 --> 00:59:42,179
[SPEAKER_01] nestalo.

1386
00:59:42,179 --> 00:59:42,780
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerojatno,

1387
00:59:42,780 --> 00:59:44,019
[SPEAKER_01] od prevelikog umora,

1388
00:59:44,019 --> 00:59:45,639
[SPEAKER_01] koliko god se ti trudiš.

1389
00:59:45,639 --> 00:59:46,559
[SPEAKER_01] Jer sam htjela uvijek

1390
00:59:46,559 --> 00:59:48,639
[SPEAKER_01] da pravedno svima bude jednako.

1391
00:59:48,639 --> 00:59:50,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ipak su tu

1392
00:59:50,199 --> 00:59:52,260
[SPEAKER_01] sastojci kao

1393
00:59:52,260 --> 00:59:54,460
[SPEAKER_01] različite komponente

1394
00:59:54,460 --> 00:59:56,539
[SPEAKER_01] i imunoglobulina

1395
00:59:56,539 --> 00:59:58,539
[SPEAKER_01] koje mislim da ne može biti

1396
00:59:58,539 --> 01:00:00,460
[SPEAKER_01] u formuli kao u maminom mlijeku.

1397
01:00:00,460 --> 01:00:02,340
[SPEAKER_00] Da, razmišljam kako uopće.

1398
01:00:02,340 --> 01:00:03,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, kad su blizanci pa nekako,

1399
01:00:03,840 --> 01:00:06,039
[SPEAKER_00] ali kad je troje,

1400
01:00:06,039 --> 01:00:09,320
[SPEAKER_00] kako odrediti da bude pošteno,

1401
01:00:09,320 --> 01:00:10,980
[SPEAKER_00] vjerojatno je izazovno,

1402
01:00:10,980 --> 01:00:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] samo po sebi,

1403
01:00:12,000 --> 01:00:12,880
[SPEAKER_00] ta brojka

1404
01:00:12,880 --> 01:00:13,820
[SPEAKER_00] i onda sve dalje,

1405
01:00:13,820 --> 01:00:14,559
[SPEAKER_00] puta tri,

1406
01:00:14,559 --> 01:00:16,400
[SPEAKER_00] svaka čast.

1407
01:00:16,400 --> 01:00:18,139
[SPEAKER_00] Svaka čast svakoj mami.

1408
01:00:18,139 --> 01:00:20,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ali pogotovo sa blizancima.

1409
01:00:20,460 --> 01:00:23,519
[SPEAKER_00] A onda tek sa troje odjednom uopće.

1410
01:00:24,159 --> 01:00:26,019
[SPEAKER_00] Što vam je bilo ovako najzazovnije?

1411
01:00:26,019 --> 01:00:28,719
[SPEAKER_01] Pa najzazovnije ti je u početku

1412
01:00:28,719 --> 01:00:29,219
[SPEAKER_01] i ti si,

1413
01:00:29,219 --> 01:00:30,980
[SPEAKER_01] to mi je bila jedna faza

1414
01:00:30,980 --> 01:00:32,980
[SPEAKER_01] kada mi jedna moja čer

1415
01:00:32,980 --> 01:00:33,980
[SPEAKER_01] jedno vrijeme

1416
01:00:33,980 --> 01:00:35,659
[SPEAKER_01] nije htjela jesti dobro.

1417
01:00:35,659 --> 01:00:36,340
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, tebe,

1418
01:00:36,340 --> 01:00:37,559
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim ko roditelju,

1419
01:00:37,559 --> 01:00:38,500
[SPEAKER_01] najveća koma,

1420
01:00:38,500 --> 01:00:39,460
[SPEAKER_01] ako dijete ima

1421
01:00:39,460 --> 01:00:40,739
[SPEAKER_01] tri, četiri mjeseca

1422
01:00:40,739 --> 01:00:41,920
[SPEAKER_01] i neće jesti.

1423
01:00:42,039 --> 01:00:42,960
[SPEAKER_01] nešto mu smeta.

1424
01:00:42,960 --> 01:00:43,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da li flašica,

1425
01:00:43,960 --> 01:00:44,639
[SPEAKER_01] mlijeko,

1426
01:00:44,639 --> 01:00:46,280
[SPEAKER_01] duda okreće se,

1427
01:00:46,280 --> 01:00:46,860
[SPEAKER_01] ne pojede

1428
01:00:46,860 --> 01:00:48,179
[SPEAKER_01] koliko bi ti htio

1429
01:00:48,179 --> 01:00:49,280
[SPEAKER_01] i tako.

1430
01:00:49,280 --> 01:00:50,099
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da mi je,

1431
01:00:50,099 --> 01:00:51,699
[SPEAKER_01] to mi je bilo onako,

1432
01:00:51,699 --> 01:00:52,559
[SPEAKER_01] recimo,

1433
01:00:52,559 --> 01:00:53,480
[SPEAKER_01] najstresnije.

1434
01:00:53,480 --> 01:00:55,300
[SPEAKER_01] Onda jedan infekt

1435
01:00:55,300 --> 01:00:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] koji je bio

1436
01:00:56,000 --> 01:00:57,719
[SPEAKER_01] u dobi od nekih

1437
01:00:57,719 --> 01:00:59,420
[SPEAKER_01] šest mjeseci

1438
01:00:59,420 --> 01:01:00,280
[SPEAKER_01] kada je bio

1439
01:01:00,280 --> 01:01:02,260
[SPEAKER_01] početni bronhitis,

1440
01:01:02,460 --> 01:01:03,840
[SPEAKER_01] ali to smo uspjeli

1441
01:01:03,840 --> 01:01:05,480
[SPEAKER_01] kući ovoga

1442
01:01:05,480 --> 01:01:06,099
[SPEAKER_01] izvući,

1443
01:01:06,099 --> 01:01:07,440
[SPEAKER_01] znači to pištanje

1444
01:01:07,440 --> 01:01:08,119
[SPEAKER_01] po noći

1445
01:01:08,119 --> 01:01:08,619
[SPEAKER_01] i tako,

1446
01:01:08,619 --> 01:01:09,219
[SPEAKER_01] tako da.

1447
01:01:09,219 --> 01:01:12,199
[SPEAKER_00] Je li vas bilo nekad strah

1448
01:01:12,199 --> 01:01:13,519
[SPEAKER_00] da će vam

1449
01:01:13,519 --> 01:01:14,860
[SPEAKER_00] to

1450
01:01:14,860 --> 01:01:17,639
[SPEAKER_00] utjecati negativno

1451
01:01:17,639 --> 01:01:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] na

1452
01:01:18,000 --> 01:01:19,880
[SPEAKER_00] karijeru?

1453
01:01:19,880 --> 01:01:22,059
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ste bili

1454
01:01:22,059 --> 01:01:23,059
[SPEAKER_00] u glavi s tim

1455
01:01:23,059 --> 01:01:24,099
[SPEAKER_00] općenito?

1456
01:01:24,099 --> 01:01:24,980
[SPEAKER_00] Razmišljam,

1457
01:01:24,980 --> 01:01:25,719
[SPEAKER_00] jer možda sad

1458
01:01:25,719 --> 01:01:27,019
[SPEAKER_00] neka liječnica

1459
01:01:27,019 --> 01:01:27,800
[SPEAKER_00] na vaše mjesto

1460
01:01:27,800 --> 01:01:29,579
[SPEAKER_00] od prije 22-23 godine

1461
01:01:29,579 --> 01:01:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] trudna recimo

1462
01:01:31,119 --> 01:01:34,039
[SPEAKER_00] i da se sad

1463
01:01:34,039 --> 01:01:35,320
[SPEAKER_00] tipa direktno

1464
01:01:35,320 --> 01:01:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] njoj obraćate?

1465
01:01:36,199 --> 01:01:37,719
[SPEAKER_00] Možda je u strahu,

1466
01:01:37,719 --> 01:01:38,440
[SPEAKER_00] kako, što?

1467
01:01:38,440 --> 01:01:40,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je specializacija

1468
01:01:40,159 --> 01:01:41,059
[SPEAKER_00] tek tu negdje

1469
01:01:41,059 --> 01:01:41,860
[SPEAKER_00] u zraku,

1470
01:01:41,860 --> 01:01:43,699
[SPEAKER_00] malo,

1471
01:01:43,699 --> 01:01:44,760
[SPEAKER_00] ako vam nije teško

1472
01:01:44,760 --> 01:01:45,900
[SPEAKER_00] vratiti se u to vrijeme?

1473
01:01:45,900 --> 01:01:47,300
[SPEAKER_01] Nije uopće.

1474
01:01:47,300 --> 01:01:47,739
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1475
01:01:47,739 --> 01:01:48,760
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam tada bila

1476
01:01:48,760 --> 01:01:50,619
[SPEAKER_01] na zadnjoj godini

1477
01:01:50,619 --> 01:01:52,019
[SPEAKER_01] ovoga svoje

1478
01:01:52,019 --> 01:01:52,900
[SPEAKER_01] specializacije

1479
01:01:52,900 --> 01:01:53,900
[SPEAKER_01] iz pediatrije.

1480
01:01:53,900 --> 01:01:55,179
[SPEAKER_01] Bila sam sigurna,

1481
01:01:55,179 --> 01:01:56,099
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam znala točno

1482
01:01:56,099 --> 01:01:56,659
[SPEAKER_01] što hoću,

1483
01:01:56,659 --> 01:01:57,539
[SPEAKER_01] bila sam sigurna

1484
01:01:57,539 --> 01:01:58,260
[SPEAKER_01] da to želim

1485
01:01:58,260 --> 01:01:58,960
[SPEAKER_01] završiti

1486
01:01:58,960 --> 01:02:00,360
[SPEAKER_01] i želim biti pediatra

1487
01:02:00,360 --> 01:02:01,179
[SPEAKER_01] ili to želim od kad

1488
01:02:01,179 --> 01:02:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] znam za sebe.

1489
01:02:01,960 --> 01:02:03,480
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to je bilo

1490
01:02:03,480 --> 01:02:04,340
[SPEAKER_01] neupitno

1491
01:02:04,340 --> 01:02:06,360
[SPEAKER_01] i stvar je samo

1492
01:02:06,360 --> 01:02:07,300
[SPEAKER_01] se posložiti.

1493
01:02:07,300 --> 01:02:08,559
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, oni kad su

1494
01:02:08,559 --> 01:02:11,139
[SPEAKER_01] bili malo veći

1495
01:02:11,139 --> 01:02:12,619
[SPEAKER_01] da mogu biti,

1496
01:02:12,619 --> 01:02:13,679
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo reći sami,

1497
01:02:13,679 --> 01:02:15,179
[SPEAKER_01] ja čak nisam koristila

1498
01:02:15,179 --> 01:02:16,519
[SPEAKER_01] poredni dopust

1499
01:02:16,519 --> 01:02:17,639
[SPEAKER_01] pune tri godine

1500
01:02:17,639 --> 01:02:19,079
[SPEAKER_01] nego dvije.

1501
01:02:19,079 --> 01:02:20,059
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, da vidiš

1502
01:02:20,059 --> 01:02:20,820
[SPEAKER_01] da neka osoba

1503
01:02:20,820 --> 01:02:21,199
[SPEAKER_01] može

1504
01:02:21,199 --> 01:02:22,340
[SPEAKER_01] biti s njima,

